        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>Release Date: May 2, 2008 [EBook #25288]</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>Language: Chinese</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">*** START OF THIS PROJECT GUTENBERG EBOOK CLASSIC OF THE MOUNTAINS AND SEAS ***</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Produced by Ting-wei You</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">南山經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">南山經之首曰鵲山。其首曰招搖之山，臨于西海之上，多桂，多金玉。有草焉，其狀如 韭而青華，其名曰祝余，食之不飢。有木焉，其狀如谷而黑理，其華四照，其名曰迷谷，佩 之不迷。有獸焉，其狀如禺而白耳，伏行人走，其名曰【□生】【□生】，食之善走。麗 【上鹿下旨】之水出焉，而西流注于海，其中多育沛，佩之無瘕疾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百里，曰堂庭之山，多【木炎】木，多白猿，多水玉，多黃金。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百八十里，曰【□爰】翼之山，其中多怪獸，水多怪魚，多白玉，多蝮蟲，多怪 蛇，多怪木，不可以上！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百七十里，曰?陽之山，其陽多赤金，其陰多白金。又獸焉，其狀如馬而白首， 其文如虎，而赤尾，其音如謠，其名曰鹿蜀，佩之宜子孫。怪水出焉，而東流注于憲翼之 水。其中多玄龜，其狀如龜而鳥首虺尾，其名曰旋龜，其音如判木，佩之不聾，可以為底。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百里柢山，多水，無草木。有魚焉，其狀如牛，陵居，蛇尾有翼，其羽在【魚 去】下，其音如留牛，其名曰鮭，冬死而複生，食之無腫疾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東四百里，曰擅爰之山，多水，無草木，不可以上。有獸焉，其狀如狸而有髦，其名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>曰類，自為牝牡，食者不妒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百里，曰基山，其陽多玉，其陰多怪木。有獸焉，其狀如羊，九尾四耳，其目在 背，其名曰【左□右上甫右下寸】【□也】，佩之不畏。有鳥焉，其狀如雞而三首、六目、 六足、三翼，其名曰【尚鳥】【付鳥】，食之無臥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百里，曰青丘之山，其陽多玉，其陰多青【左丹右上隹右下又】。有獸焉，其狀 如狐而九尾，其音如嬰兒，能食人，食者不蠱。有鳥焉，其狀如鳩，其音若呵，名曰灌灌， 佩之不惑。英水出焉，南海注于即翼之澤。其中多赤【魚需】，其狀如魚而人面，其音如鴦 鴛，食之不疥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百五十里，曰箕尾之山，其尾【駿去馬換足】于東海，多沙石。【□方】水出 焉，而南流注于【□育】，其中多白玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡鵲山之首，自招搖之出，以至箕尾之山，丸十山，二千九百五十里。其神狀皆鳥身而 龍首。其祠之禮；毛用一璋玉瘞，糈用【禾余】米，一壁稻米，白菅為席。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>南次二經之首，曰櫃山，西臨流黃，北望諸【囟比】，東望長右。英水出焉，西南流注 于赤水，其中多白玉，多丹粟。有獸焉，其狀如豚，有距，其音如狗吠，其名曰狸力，見則 其縣多土功。有鳥焉，其狀如鴟而人手，其音如痺，其名曰【朱鳥】，其名自號也，見則其 縣多放土。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東南四百五十里，曰長右之山，無草木，多水。有獸焉，其狀如禺而四耳，其名長右， 其音如吟，見則郡縣大水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百四十里，曰堯光之山，其陽多玉，其陰多金。有獸焉，其狀如人而彘鬣，穴居 而冬蟄，其名曰猾囗，其音如斫木，見則縣有大繇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百五百里，曰羽山，其下多水，其上多雨，無草木，多蝮蟲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百七十里。曰瞿父之山，無草木，多金玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東四百里，曰句余之山，無草木，多金玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰浮玉之山，北望具區東望諸【囟比】。有獸焉，其狀如虎而牛尾，其音 如吠犬，其名曰彘，是食人。苕水出于其陰，北流注于具區。其中多【上此下魚】魚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰成山，四方而三壇，其上多金玉，其下多青【左丹右上隹右下又】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【外門內豕】水出焉，而南流注于【上虎頭下乎】勺，其中多黃金。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰會稽之山，四方，其上多金玉，其下多【石夫】石。勺水出焉，而南流 注于溴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰夷山。無草木，多沙石。溴水出焉，而南注于列塗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰僕勾之山，其上多金玉，其下多草木，無鳥獸，無水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰咸陰之山，無草木，無水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東四百里，曰洵山，其陽多金，其陰多玉。有獸焉，其狀如羊而無口，不可殺也，其 名曰【羊患】。洵水出焉，而南流注于閼之澤，其中多芘蠃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東四百里，曰【上虎頭下乎】勺之山，其上多梓【木丹】，其下多荊杞。滂水出焉， 而東流注于海。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰區吳之山，無草木，多沙石。鹿水出焉，而南流注于滂水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰鹿吳之山，上無草木，多金石。澤更之水出焉，而南流注于滂水。水有 獸焉，名曰蠱雕，其狀如雕而有角，其音如嬰兒之音，是食人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東五百里，曰漆吳之山，無草木，多博石，無玉。處于東海，望丘山，其光載出開車 入，是惟日次。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡南次二經之首，自櫃山于漆吳之山，凡十七山，七千二百里。其神狀皆龍身而島首。 其祠：毛用一壁瘞，糈用【禾余】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>南次三經之首，曰天下虞之山，其下多水，不可以上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東五百里，曰禱過之山，其上多金玉，其下多犀、兕，多象。有鳥焉，其狀如【交鳥】 而白首，三足、人面，其名曰瞿如，其鳴自號也。浪水出焉，而南流注于海。其中有虎蛟， 其狀魚身而蛇尾，其音如鴛鴦，食者不腫，可以已痔。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰丹穴之山，其上多金玉。丹水出焉，而南流注于渤海。有鳥焉，其狀如 雞，五採而文，名曰鳳凰，首文曰德，翼文曰義，背文曰禮，膺文曰仁，腹文曰信。是鳥 也，飲食自然，自歌自舞，見則天下安寧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰發爽之山，無草木，多水，多白猿。慼牖[桑□□狹髯□誆澈！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東四百里，至于旄山之尾。其南有谷，曰育遺，多怪鳥，凱風自是出。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東四百里，至于非出山之首，其上多金玉，無水，其下多蝮蟲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰陽夾之山，無草木，多水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰灌湘之山，上多木，無草；多怪鳥，無獸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰雞山，其上多金，其下多丹【左丹右上隹右下又】。黑水山焉，而南流 注于海。其中有鯖魚，其狀如鮒而彘毛，其音如豚，見則天下大旱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東四百里，曰令丘之山，無草木，多火。其南有谷焉，曰中谷，條風自是出。有鳥 焉，其狀職梟，人而四目而有耳，其名曰【禺頁】，其鳴自號也，見則天下大旱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百七十里，曰崙者之山，其上多金玉，其下多青【在丹右上隹右下又】。有木 焉，其狀如谷而赤理，其汗如漆，其味如飴，食者不飢，可以釋勞，其名曰白【上□下 咎】，可以血玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百八十里，曰禺稿之山，多怪獸，多大蛇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百八十里，曰南禺之山，有上多金玉，其下多水。有穴焉，水出輒入，夏乃出， 冬則閉。佐水出焉，而東南流注于海，有鳳凰、【宛鳥】雛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡南次三經之首，自天虞之山以至南禺之山，凡一十四山，六千五百三十里。其神皆龍 身而人面。其祠皆一白狗祈，糈用【禾余】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>右南經之山志，大小凡四十山，萬六千三百八十里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">西山經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">西山經華山之首，曰錢來之山，其上多松，其下多洗石。有獸焉，其狀如羊而馬尾，名 曰【羊咸】羊，其脂可以已臘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西四十五里，曰松果之山。囗水出焉，北流注于渭，其中多銅。有鳥焉，其名曰【蟲 鳥】渠其狀如山雞，黑身赤足，可以已【月暴】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西六十里，曰太華之山，削成而四方，其高五千仞，其廣十里，鳥獸莫居。有蛇焉， 名曰肥囗，六足四翼，見則天下大旱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西八十里，曰小華之山，其木多荊杞，其獸多【牛乍】牛，其陰多磬石，其陽多【王 雩】【王孚】之玉。鳥多赤【上敝下鳥】，可以御火。其草有萆荔，狀如烏韭，而生于石 上，赤緣木而生，食之已心痛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西八十里，曰符禺之山，其陽多銅，其陰多鐵。其上有木焉，名曰文莖，其實如棗， 可以已聾。其草多條，其狀如葵，而赤華黃實，如嬰兒舌，食之使人不惑。符禺之水出焉， 而北流注于渭。其獸多蔥聾，其狀如羊而赤鬣。其鳥多【民鳥】，其狀如翠而赤喙，可以御 火。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西六十里，曰石脆之山，其木多棕【木丹】，其草多條，其狀如韭，而白華黑實，食 之已疥。其陽多【王雩】【王孚】之玉，其陰多銅。灌水出焉，而北流注于禺水。其中有流 赭，以塗牛馬無病。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西七十里，曰英山，其上多?囗，其陰多鐵，其陽多赤金。禺水出焉，北流注于招 水，其中多【魚豐】魚，其狀如鱉，其音如羊。其陽多箭【上竹下媚】，獸多【牛乍】牛、 【羊咸】羊。有鳥焉，其狀如鶉，黃身而赤喙，其名曰肥遺，食之已癘，可以殺蟲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西五十二里，曰竹山，其上多喬木，其陰多鐵。有草焉，其名曰黃囗，其狀如樗，其 葉如麻，白華而赤實，其狀如赭，浴之已疥，又可以已【月付】。竹水出焉，北流注于渭， 其陽多竹箭，多蒼玉。丹水出焉，東南流注于洛水，其中多水玉，多人魚。有獸下，其狀如 豚而白毛，大如【上竹左下幹右下幹】而黑端，名曰豪彘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西百二十里，曰浮山，多盼木，枳葉而無傷，木蟲居之。有草焉，名曰薰草，麻葉而 方莖，赤華而黑實，臭如蘼蕪，佩之可以已癘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西七十里，曰囗次之山，漆水出焉，北流注于渭。其上多【木或】囗，其下多竹箭， 其陰多赤銅，其陽多嬰垣之玉。有獸焉，其狀如禺而長臂，善投，其名曰囂。有鳥焉，其狀 如梟，人面而一足，曰橐【上非下巴】，冬見夏蟄，服之不畏雷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西百五十里，曰時山，無草木。逐水出焉，北海注于渭，其中多水玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西百七十里，曰南山，上多丹粟。丹水出焉，北流注于渭。獸多猛豹，鳥多尸鳩。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西四百八里，曰大時之山，上多楮柞，下多?囗，陰多銀，陽多白玉。涔水出焉，北 流注于渭。清水出焉，南流注于漢水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百二十里，曰【山番】塚之山，漢水出焉，而東南流注于沔；囂水出焉，北流注 于湯水。其上多桃枝【□句】端，獸多犀兕熊羆，鳥多白翰赤【上敝下鳥】。有草焉，其葉 如蕙，其本如桔梗，黑華而不實，名曰【上□下骨】蓉。食之使人無子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百五十里，曰天帝之山，多棕【木丹】；下多菅蕙。有獸焉，其狀如狗，名曰溪 邊，席其皮者不蠱。有鳥焉，其狀如鶉，黑文而赤翁，名曰櫟，食之已痔。有草焉，其狀如 共葵，共其臭如蘼蕪，名曰杜衡，可以走馬，食之已癭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西南三百八十里，曰【上自下半】塗之山，薔水出焉，西流注于諸資之水；塗水出焉， 南流注于集獲之水。其陽多丹粟，其陰多銀、黃金，其上多桂木。有白石焉，其名曰囗，可 以毒鼠。有草焉，其狀如稿芨，其葉如葵赤背，名曰無條，可以毒鼠。有獸焉，其狀如鹿而 白尾，馬足人手而四角，名曰【□嬰】如。有鳥焉，其狀如鴟而人足，名曰數斯，食之已癭。 又西百八十里，曰黃山，無草木，多竹箭。盼水出焉，西流注于赤水，其中多玉。有獸 焉，其狀如牛，而蒼黑大目，其狀曰【上敏下牛】。有鳥焉，其狀如【號鳥】，青羽赤喙， 人舌能言，名曰鸚鵡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百里，曰翠山，其上多棕【木丹】，其下多竹箭，其陽多黃金、玉，其多【左三 田右鳥】，其狀如鵲，赤黑而兩四足，可以御火。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百五十里，曰【馬鬼】山，是【□享】于西海，無草木，多玉。【□妻】水出 焉，西流注于海，其中多採石、黃金，多丹粟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡西經之首，自錢來之山至于【馬鬼】山，凡十九山，二千九百五十七里。華山塚也， 其祠之禮：太牢。囗山神也，祠之用燭，齋百日以百犧，瘞用百瑜，湯其酒百樽，嬰以百 【王圭】百壁。其余十七山之屬，皆毛【牛全】用一羊祠之。燭者，百草之未灰，白【下 下席】採等純之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西次二經之首，曰鈐山，其上多銅，其下多玉，其木多?囗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西二百里，曰泰冒之山，其陽多玉，其陰多鐵。浴水出焉，東流注于河，其中多藻玉， 多白蛇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西一百七十里，曰數歷之山，其上多黃金，其下多銀，其木多黃金，其下多銀，其木 多?囗，其鳥多鸚鵡。楚水出焉，而南流注于渭，其中多白珠。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西百五十里高山，其上多銀，其下多青碧、雄黃，其木多棕，其草多竹。涇水出焉， 而東流注于渭，其中多馨石、青碧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西南三百里，曰女床之山，其陽多赤銅，其陰多石涅，其獸多虎豹犀兕。有鳥焉，其狀 如翟而五採文，名曰鸞鳥，見則天下安寧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百里，曰龍首之山，其陽多黃金，其陽多鐵。苕水出焉，東海流注于涇水，其中 多美玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百里，曰鹿台之山，其上多白玉，其下多銀，其獸多【牛乍】牛、【羊咸】羊、 白豪。有鳥焉，其狀如雄雞自叫也，見則有兵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西南二里，曰鳥危之山，其陽多馨石，其陰多檀楮，其中多女床。鳥危之水出焉，西流 注于赤水，其中多丹粟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西四百里，曰小次之山，其上多白玉，其下多赤銅。有獸焉其狀如猿，而白首赤足， 名曰朱厭，見則大兵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百里，曰大次之山，其陽多堊，其陰多碧，其獸多【牛乍】羊、【下鹿中雨下三 口】羊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西四百里，曰薰吳之山，無草木，多金玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西四百里，曰囗陽之山，其木多稷、【木丹】、豫章，其獸多犀、兕、虎、【□ 勺】、【牛乍】牛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百五十里，曰眾獸之山，其上多【王雩】【王孚】之玉，其下多檀楮，多黃金， 其獸多犀兕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西五百里，曰皇人之山，其上多金玉，其下多青雄黃。皇水出焉，西流注于赤水，其 中多丹粟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百里，曰中皇之山，其上多黃金，其下多蕙、棠。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百五十里，曰西皇之山，其陽多黃金，其陰多鐵，其獸多麋、鹿、【牛乍】牛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百里五十里，曰萊山，其木多檀楮，其鳥多羅羅，是食人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡西次二經之首，自鈐山至于萊山，凡十七山，四千一百四十里。其十神者，皆人面而 馬身。其七神皆人面而牛身，四足而一臂，操杖以行，是為飛獸之神。其祠之，毛用少牢， 白菅為席。其十輩神者，其祠之毛一雄雞，鈐而不糈：毛採。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西次三經之首，曰崇吾之山，在河之南，北望塚遂，南望【遙去□】之澤，西望帝之捕 獸之丘，東望【蟲焉】淵。有木焉，員葉而白【木付】，赤華而黑理，其實如枳，食之宜子 孫。有獸焉，其狀如鳧，而一翼一日，相得乃飛，名曰蠻蠻，見則天下大水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西北三百里，曰長沙之山。【□此】水出焉，北流注于【□幼】水，無草木，多青雄黃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西北三百七十里，曰不周之山。北望諸【蟲焉】之山，臨彼岳崇之山，東望【□幼】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>澤，河水所潛也，其原渾渾泡泡。爰有嘉果，其實如桃，其葉如棗，黃華而赤【木付】，食 之不勞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西北四百二十里，曰【上山中大下土】山，其上多丹木，員葉而赤莖，黃華而赤實， 其味如飴，食之不飢。丹水出焉，西流注于稷澤，其中多白玉。是有玉膏，其原沸沸湯湯， 黃帝是食是饗。是生玄玉。玉膏所出，以灌丹木，丹木五歲，五色乃清，五味乃馨。黃帝乃 取【上山中大下土】山之玉榮，而投之鐘山之陽。瑾瑜之玉為良，堅粟精密，濁澤有而色。 五色發作，以和柔剛。天地鬼神，是食是饗；君子服之，以御為祥。自【上山中大下土】山 至于鐘山，四百六十里，其間盡澤也。是多奇鳥、怪獸、奇魚，皆異物焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西北四百二十里，曰鐘山。其子曰鼓，其狀如人面而龍身，是與欽【丕鳥】殺葆江于 昆崙之陽，帝乃戮之鐘山之東曰【山加鷂去鳥】崖。欽【丕鳥】化為大鶚，其狀如雕而墨文 曰首，赤喙而虎爪，其音如晨鵠，見則有大兵；鼓亦化為【皴去皮加鳥】鳥，其狀如鴟，赤 足而直喙，黃文而白首，其音如鵠，見即其邑大旱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西百八十里，曰泰器之山。觀水出焉，西流注于流沙。是多文鰩魚，狀如鯉里，魚身 而鳥翼，蒼文而白首赤喙，常行西海，游于東海，以夜飛。其音如鸞雞，其味酸甘，食之已 狂，見則天下大穰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百二十里，曰槐江之山。丘時之水出焉，而北流注于【□幼】水。其中多蠃其上 金青雄黃，多藏琅【王千】、黃金、玉，其陽多丹粟。其了有多採黃金銀。實惟帝之平圃， 神英招司之，其狀馬身而人面，虎文而鳥翼，徇于四海，其音如榴。南望昆崙，其光熊熊， 其氣魂魂。西望大澤，后稷所潛也。其中多玉，其陰多【木加鷂去鳥】木之有若。北望諸 【囟此】，槐鬼離崙居之，鷹【顫去頁加鳥】之所宅也。東望恆山四成，有窮鬼居之，各在 一搏。爰有淫水，其清洛洛。有天神焉，其狀如牛，而八足二首馬尾，其音如勃皇，見則其 邑有兵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西南四百里，曰昆崙之丘，是實惟帝之下都，神陸吾司之。其神狀虎身而九尾，人面而 虎爪；是神也，司天之九部及帝之囿時，有獸焉，其狀如羊而四角，名曰土螻，是食人。有 鳥焉，其狀如蜂，大如鴛鴦，名曰欽原，【上若下兩蟲】鳥獸則死，【上若下兩蟲】木則 枯，有鳥焉，其名曰鶉鳥，是司帝之百服。有木焉，其狀如棠，黃華赤實，其味如李而無 核，名曰沙棠，可以御水，食之使人不溺。有草焉，名曰【上□下賓】草，其狀如葵，其味 如蔥，食之已勞。河水出焉，而南流注于無達。赤水出焉，而東南流注于泛天之水。洋水出 焉，而西南流注于醜塗之水。墨水出焉，而四海流注于大桿。是多怪鳥獸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百七十里，曰樂游之山。桃水出焉，西流注于稷澤，是多白玉，其中多【魚骨】 魚，其狀如蛇而四足，是食魚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西水行四百里，曰流沙，二百里至于嬴母之山，神長乘司之，是天之九德也。其神狀如 人而豹尾。其上多玉，其下多青石而無水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西北三百五十里，曰玉山，是西王母所居也。西王母其狀如人，豹尾虎齒而善嘯，蓬 發戴勝，是司天之厲及五殘。有獸焉，其狀如犬而豹文，其角如牛，其名曰狡，其音如吠 犬，見則其國大穰。有鳥焉，其狀如翟而赤，名曰勝遇，是食魚，其音如錄，見則其國大水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西四百八十里，曰軒轅之丘，無草木。洵水出焉，南流注于黑水，其中多丹粟，多青 雄黃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百里，曰積石之山，其下有石門，河水冒以西流，是山也，萬物無不有焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百里，曰長留之山，其神白帝少昊居之。其獸皆文尾，其鳥皆文首。是多文玉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>石。實惟員神【石鬼】氏之宮。是神也，主司反景。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百八十里，曰章莪之山，無草木，多瑤碧。所為甚怪。有獸焉，其狀如赤豹，五 尾一角，其音如擊石，其名如猙。有鳥焉，其狀如鶴，一足，赤文青質而白喙，名曰畢文， 其鳴自叫也，見則其邑有【□為】火。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百里，曰陰山。濁浴之水出焉，而南流注于番澤，其中多文貝。有獸焉，其狀如 狸而白首，名曰天狗，其音如榴榴，可以御凶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百里，曰符惕之山，其上多棕【木丹】，下多金玉。神江疑居之。是山也，多怪 雨，風云之所出也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百二十里，曰三危之山，三青鳥居之。是山也，廣員百里。其上有獸焉，其狀如 牛，白身四角，其豪如披蓑，其名曰【彳敖】【彳因】，是食有。有鳥焉，一首而三身，其 狀如【樂鳥】，其名曰鴟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西一百九十里，曰【馬鬼】山，其上多玉而無石。神耆童居之，其音常如鐘磬。其下 多積蛇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百五十里，曰天山，多金玉，有青雄黃。英水出焉，而西南流注于湯谷。有神 焉，基狀如黃囊，赤如丹水，六足四翼，渾敦無而目，是識歌舞，實為帝江也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百九十里，曰【□幼】山，神蓐收居之。其上多嬰短之玉，其陽多瑾瑜之玉，其 陰多青雄黃。是山也，西望日之所入，其氣員，神紅光之所司也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西水行百里，至于翼望之山，無草木，多金玉。有獸焉，其狀如狸，一日而三尾，名曰 囗，其音如囗百聲，是可以御凶，服之已癉。有鳥焉，其狀如烏，三首六尾而善笑，名曰 【奇鳥】【余鳥】，服之使人不厭，又可以御凶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡西次三經之首，崇吾之山至于翼望之山，凡二十三山，六千七百四十四里。其神狀皆 羊身人面。其祠之禮，用一吉玉瘞，糈用稷米。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西次四經之首，曰陰山，上多楮，無石，其草多茆、蕃。陰水出焉，西流注于洛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>北五十里，曰勞山，多茈草。弱水出焉，而西流注于洛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西五十里，曰罷父之山，洱水出焉，而西流注于洛，其中多茈、碧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>北七十里，曰中山，其上多楮柞，其下多?囗，其陽多金玉。區水出焉，而江流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>北二百里，曰鳥山，其上多桑，其焉多楮，其陰多鐵，其陽多玉。辱水出焉，而東流注 于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北百二里，曰上申之山，上無草木，而多硌石，下多榛【木苦】，獸多白鹿。其鳥多 當扈，其狀如雉，以其髯飛，食之不【目旬】目。湯水出焉，東流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北百八十里，曰諸次之山，諸次之水出焉，而東流注于河。是山也，多木無草，鳥獸 莫居，是多眾蛇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北百八十里，曰號山，其木多漆、棕，其草多藥、芎【上□下窮】。多冷石。端水出 焉，而東流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百二十里，曰盂山，其陰多鐵，其陽多銅，其獸多白狼白虎，其鳥多白雉白翟。 生水出焉，而東流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西二百五十里，曰白於之山，上多松柏，下多櫟檀，其獸多【牛乍】牛、【羊咸】羊， 其鳥多【號鳥】。洛水出于其陽，而東流注于渭；夾水出于其陰，東流注于生水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西北三百里，曰申首之山，無草木，冬夏雪。申水出于其上。潛于其下，是多白玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西五十五里，曰涇谷之山。涇水出焉，東南流注于渭，是多白金白玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西百二十里，曰剛山，多柒木，多【王雩】【王孚】之玉。剛水出焉，北流注于渭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>是多神[光鬼】，其狀人面獸身，一足一手，其音如欽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百里，至剛山之尾。洛水出焉，而北流注于河。其中多蠻蠻，其狀鼠身而鱉首， 其音如吠犬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百五十里，曰英【革是】之山，上多漆木，下多金玉，鳥獸盡白。【□宛】水出 焉，而北流注于陵羊之澤。是多冉遺之魚，魚身蛇首六足，其目如觀耳，食之使人不瞇，可 以御凶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百里，曰中曲之山，其陽多玉，其陰多雄黃、白玉及金。有獸焉，其狀如馬而白 身黑尾，一角，虎牙爪，音如鼓音，其名曰【馬交】，是食虎豹，可以御兵。有木焉，其狀 如棠，而員葉赤實，實大如木瓜，名曰杯木，食之多力。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百六十里，曰【圭□】山。其上有獸焉，其狀如牛，【蟲胃】毛，名曰窮奇，音 如【□皋】狗，是食人。【□蒙】水出焉，南流注于洋水，其中多黃貝；嬴魚，魚身而鳥 翼，音如鴛鴦，見則其邑大水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百二十里，曰鳥鼠同穴之山，其上多白虎、白玉。渭水出焉，而東流注于河。其 中多□魚，其狀如囗魚，動則其邑有大兵。濫水出于其西，西流注于漢水，多【上如下魚】 【左魚右比】之魚，其狀如覆銚，鳥首而魚翼，音如磬石之聲，是生珠玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西南三百六十里，曰崦嵫之山，其上多丹木，其葉如楮，其實大如瓜，赤符而黑理，食 之已癉，可以御火。其陽多龜，其陰多玉。苕水出焉，而西流注于海，其中多砥勵。有獸 焉，其狀馬身而鳥翼，入面蛇尾，是好舉人，名曰孰湖。有鳥焉，其狀如【號鳥】而人面， 【蟲隹】身犬尾，其名自號也，見則其邑大旱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡西次四經自陰山以下，至于崦嵫之山，凡十九山，三千六百八十里。其神祠禮，皆用 一白雞祈，糈以稻米，白菅為席。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>右西經之山，凡七十七山，一萬七千五百一十七里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">北山經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">北山經之首，曰單狐之山，多機木，其上多華草。逢【□逢】水出焉，而西流注于【 幼】水，其中多芘石文石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百五十里，曰求如之山，其上多玉，無草木。滑水出焉，而西流注于諸囗之水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>其中多滑魚。其狀如【魚單】，赤背，其音如梧，食之已疣。其中多水馬，其狀如馬，文臂 牛尾，其音如呼。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百里，曰帶山，其上多玉，其下多青碧。有獸焉，其狀如馬，一角有錯，其名曰 囗疏，可以闢火。有鳥焉，其狀如烏，五採而赤文，名曰【奇鳥】【余鳥】，是自為牝牡， 食之不疽。彭水出焉，而西流注于芘湖之水，中多囗魚，其狀如雞而赤毛，三尾六足四首， 其音如鵲，食之可以已憂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北四百里，曰譙明之山。譙水出焉，西流注于河。其中多何羅之魚，一首而十身，其 音如吠犬，食之已癰。有獸焉，其狀如【豸亙】而赤毫，其音如榴榴，名曰孟槐，可以御 凶。是山也，無草木，多青雄黃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百五十里，曰涿光之山。囂水出焉，而西流注于河。其中多囗囗【同習】之魚， 其狀如鵲而十翼，鱗皆在羽端，其音如鵲，可以御火，食之不癉。其上多松柏，其下多棕 囗，其獸多囗羊，其鳥多蕃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百八十里，曰虢山，其上多漆，其下多桐椐。其陽多玉，其陰多鐵。伊水出焉， 西流注于河。其獸多橐駝，其鳥多窩，狀如鼠而鳥翼，其音如羊，可以御兵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北四百里，至于虢山之尾，其上多玉而無石。魚水出焉，西流注于河，其中多文貝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百里，曰丹熏之山，其上多樗柏，其草多韭韭，多丹囗。熏水出焉，而西流注于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>棠水。有獸焉，其狀如鼠，而菟首麋身，其音如【□皋】犬，以其尾飛，名曰耳鼠，食之不 【月採】，又可以御百毒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百八十里，曰石者之山，其上無草木，多瑤碧。【□此】水出焉，西流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有獸焉，其狀如豹，而文題白身，名曰孟極，是善伏，其鳴自呼。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北百一十里，曰邊春之山，多蔥、葵、韭、桃、李。杠水出焉，而西流注于【□幼】 澤。有獸焉，其狀如禺而文身，善笑，見人則臥，名曰幽【安鳥】，其鳴自呼。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百里，曰蔓聯之山，其上無草木，有獸焉，其狀如禺而有鬣，牛尾、文臂、馬 【足廠虎】，見人則呼，名曰足訾，其鳴自呼。有鳥焉，群居而朋飛，其毛如雌雉，名曰 【交鳥】，其鳴自呼，食之已風。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北八百里，曰單張之山，其上無草木。有獸焉，其狀如豹而長尾，人首而牛耳，一 目，名曰諸犍，善吒，行則銜其尾。有鳥焉，其狀如雉，而文首、白翼、黃足，名曰白【夜 鳥】，食之已嗌痛，可以已【□制】。櫟水出焉，在而南流注于杠水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百二十里，曰灌題之山，其上多樗柘，其下多流沙，多砥。有獸焉，其狀如牛而 白尾，其音如【□交】，名曰那父。有鳥焉，其狀如雌雉而人面，見人則躍，名曰竦斯，其 鳴自呼也。匠韓之水出焉，而西流注于【□幼】澤，其中多磁石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百里，曰潘侯之山，其上多松柏，其下多榛【木苦】，其陽多玉，其陰多鐵。有 獸焉，基狀如牛，而四節生毛，或曰旄牛。邊水出焉，而南流注于櫟澤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百三十里，曰小咸之山，無草木，冬夏有雪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>北二百八十里，曰大咸之山，無草木，其下多玉。是山也，四方，不可以上。有蛇名曰 長蛇，其毛如彘豪，其音如鼓柝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百二十里，曰敦薨之山，其上多棕【木丹】，其下多茈草。敦薨之水出焉，而西 流注于【□幼】澤。出于昆崙之東北隅，實惟河原。其中多赤鮭，其獸多兕，旄牛，其鳥多 柝鳩。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百里，曰少咸之山，無草木，多青碧。有獸焉，其狀如牛，而赤身、人面、馬 足，名曰窺窳，其音如嬰兒，是食人。敦水出焉，東流注于雁門之水，其中多【魚市]【魚 市]之魚。食之殺人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百里，曰獄法之山。【□襄】澤之出焉，而東北流注于泰澤。其中多【魚巢】 魚，其狀如鯉而雞足，食之已疣。有獸焉，其狀如犬而人面，善投，見人則笑，其名山【 軍】，其行如風，見則天下大風。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二里，曰北岳之山，多枳棘剛木。有獸焉，其狀如牛，而四角、人、耳、彘耳，其 名曰諸懷，基音如鳴雁，是食人。諸懷之水出焉，而西流注于囂水，水中多【魚旨】魚，魚 身而犬首，其音如嬰兒，食之已狂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北百八十里，曰渾夕之山，無草木，多銅玉。囂水出焉，而西流注于海。有蛇一首兩 身，名曰肥遺，見則其國大旱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北五十里，曰北單之山，無草木，多蔥韭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北百里，曰羆差之山，無草木，多馬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北百八十里，曰北鮮之山，是多馬，鮮水出焉，而西北流注于塗吾之水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北百七十里，曰【□是】山，多馬。有獸焉，其狀如豹而文首，名曰【□幼】。【□</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>是】水出焉，而東流注于泰澤，其中多龍龜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡北山經之首，自單狐之山至于【□是】山，凡二十五山，五千四百九十里，其神皆人 面蛇身。其祠之，毛用一雄雞彘瘞，吉玉用一【王圭】，瘞而為不糈。其山北人，皆生食不 火之物。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>北次二經之首，在河之東，其首枕汾，其名曰管涔之山。其上無木而多草，其下多玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>汾水出焉，而西流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百五十里，曰少陽之山，其上多玉，其下多赤銀。酸水出焉，而東流注于汾水， 其中多美赭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北五十里，曰縣雍之山，其上多玉，其下多銅，其獸多閭麋，其鳥多白翟白【有 鳥】。晉水出焉，而東南流注于汾水。其中多【上此下魚】魚，其狀如囗而赤麟，其音如 叱，食之不驕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百里，曰狐岐之山，無草木，多青碧。勝水出焉，而東北流注于汾水，其中多蒼 玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百五十里，曰白沙山，廣員三百里，盡沙也，無草木鳥獸。鮪水出于其上，潛于 其下，是多白玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北四百里，曰爾是之山，無草木，無水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百八十里，曰狂山，無草木，是山也，冬夏有雪。狂水出焉，而西流注于浮水， 其中多美玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百八十里，曰諸余之山，其上多銅玉，其下多松柏。諸余之水出焉，而東流注于 旄水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百五十里，曰敦頭之山，其上多金玉，無草木。旄水出焉，而東流注于印澤。其 中多【馬孛】馬，牛尾而白身，一角，其音如呼。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三五十里，曰【□句】吾之山，其上多玉，其下多銅。有獸焉，其狀如羊身人面， 其目在腋下，虎齒人爪，其音如嬰兒，名曰□【號鳥】，是食人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百里，曰北囂之山，無石，其陽多玉。有獸焉，其狀如虎，而白身犬首，馬尾彘 鬣，名曰獨【□谷】。有鳥焉，其狀如烏，人面，名曰囗【冒鳥】，宵飛而晝伏，食之已 【日曷】。涔水出焉，而東流注于邛澤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百五十里，曰梁渠之山，無草木，多金玉。修水出焉，而東流注于雁門，其獸多 居暨，其狀如囗而赤毛，其音如豚。有鳥焉，其狀如誇父，四翼、一目、犬尾，名曰囂，其 音如鵲，食之已腹痛，可以止【彳同亍】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北四百里，曰姑灌之山，無草木。是山也，科夏有雪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百八十里，曰湖灌之山，其陽多玉，其陰多碧，多馬，湖灌之水出焉，而東流注 于海，其中多【魚旦】。有木器廠焉，其葉如柳而赤理。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北水行五百里，流沙三百里，至于洹山，其上多金玉。三桑生之，其樹皆無枝，其高 百仞。百果樹生之。其下多怪蛇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百里，曰敦題之山，無草木，多金玉。是【□享】于北海。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡北次二經之首，自管涔之山至于敦題之山，凡十七山，五千六百九十里。其神皆蛇身 人面。其祠；毛用一雄雞彘瘞；用一璧一【王圭】，投而不糈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>北次三經之首，曰太行之山。其首曰歸山，其上有金玉，其下有碧。有獸焉，其狀如囗 羊而四角，馬尾而有距，其名曰【馬軍】，善還，其名自【□交】有鳥焉，其狀台鵲，白 身、赤尾、六足，其名曰囗，是善驚，其鳴自【□交】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北二百里，曰龍侯之山，無草木，多金玉。決決之水出焉，而東流注于河。其中多 人魚，其狀如【魚帝】魚，四足，其音如嬰兒，食之無癡疾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北二百里，曰馬成之山，其上多文石，其陰多金玉。有獸焉，其狀如白犬而黑頭， 見人則飛，其名曰天馬，其鳴自【□交】，有鳥焉，其狀如烏，首白而身青、足黃，是名曰 【屈鳥】【居鳥】。其名自【□交】，食之不飢，可以已寓。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北七十里，曰咸山，其上有玉，其下多銅，是多松柏，草多茈草。條菅之水出焉， 而西南流注于長澤。其中多器酸，三歲一成，食之已癘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北二百里，曰天池之山，其上無草木，多文石。有獸焉，其狀如兔而鼠首，以其背 飛，其名曰飛鼠。澠水出焉，潛于其下，其中多黃堊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百里，曰陽山，其上多玉，其下多金銅。有獸焉，其狀如牛而尾，其頸【左上臣 右上又下鳥】，其狀如句瞿，其名曰領胡，其鳴自【□交】，食之已狂。有鳥焉，其狀如赤 雉，而五採以文，是自為牝牡，名曰象蛇，其名自【□交】。留水出焉，而南流注于河。其 中有囗父之魚，其狀如鮒魚，魚首而彘身，食之已嘔。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百五十里，曰賁聞之山，其上多蒼玉，其下多黃堊，多涅石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北百里，曰王屋之山，是多石。【□聯】水出焉，而西北流注于泰澤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北三百里，曰教山，其上多玉而無石。教水出焉，西流注于河，是水冬幹而夏流， 實惟幹河。其中有兩山。是山也，廣員三百步，其名曰發丸之山，其上有金玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰景山，南望鹽販之澤，北望少澤。其上多草、【上□下諸】囗，其草多 秦椒，其陰多赭，其陽多玉。有鳥焉，其狀如蛇，而四翼、六目、六足，名曰酸與，其鳴自 【□交】，見則其邑有恐。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南三百二十里，曰孟門之山，其上多蒼玉，多金，其下多黃堊，多涅石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南三百二十里，曰平山。平水出于其上，潛于其下，是多美玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二百里，曰京山，有美玉，多漆木，多竹，其陽有赤銅，其陰有玄【石肅】。高水 出焉，南流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二百里，曰蟲尾之山，其上多金玉，其下多竹，多青碧。丹水出焉，南流注于河； 薄水出焉，而東南流注于黃澤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百里，曰彭【囟比】之山，其上無草木，多金玉，其下多水。蚤林之水出焉，東 南流注于河。肥水出焉，而南流注于床水，其中多肥遺之蛇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東百八十里，曰小侯之山。明漳之水出焉，南流注于黃澤。有鳥焉，其狀如烏而白 文，名曰【古鳥】【左上羽左下白右鳥】，食之不【□爵】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百七十里，曰泰頭之山。共水出焉，南流注于池。其上多金玉，其下多竹箭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北二百里，曰軒轅之山，其上多銅，其下多竹。有鳥焉，其狀如梟白首，其名曰黃 鳥，其鳴自【□交】，食之不妒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百里，曰謁戾之山，其上多松柏，有金玉。沁水出焉，南流注于河。其東有林 焉，名曰丹林。丹林之水出焉，南流注于河。嬰侯之水出焉，北流注于汜水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東三百里，曰沮洳之山，無草木，有金玉。【□綦】水出焉，南流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百里，曰神?之山，具上有文石，其下有白蛇，有飛蟲。黃水出焉，而東流注于 洹；滏水出焉，而東流注于歐水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百里，曰發鳩之山，其上多柘水。有鳥焉，其狀如烏，文首、白喙、赤足，名曰 精衛，其鳴自【□交】。是炎帝之少女名曰女娃，女娃游于東海，溺而不返，故為精衛。常 銜西山之木石，以堙于東海。漳水出焉，東流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北百二十里，曰少山，其上有金玉，其下有銅。清漳之水出焉，東流注于濁漳之水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北二百里，曰錫山，其上多玉，其下有砥。牛首之水出焉，而東流注于滏水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百里，曰景山，有美玉。景水出焉，東南流注于海澤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北百里，曰題首之山，有玉焉，多石，無水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北百里，曰繡山，其上有玉、青碧，其木多【木旬】，其草多芍藥、芎【上□下 窮】。洧水出焉，而東流注于河，其中有囗、黽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北百二十里，曰松山。陽水出焉，東北流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北百二十里，曰敦與之山，其上無草木，有金玉。【□索】水出于其陽，而東流注于 泰陸之水；【□氐】水出于其陰，而東流注于彭水；槐水出焉，而東流注于【□氐】澤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北百七十里，曰柘山，其陽有金玉，其陰有鐵。歷聚之水出焉，而北流注于洧水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百里，曰維龍之山，其上有碧玉，其陽有金，其陰有鐵。肥水出焉，而東流注于 皋澤，其中多【上三田下石】石。敞鐵之水出焉，而北于大澤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北百八十里，曰白馬之山，其陽多石玉，其陰多鐵，多赤銅。木馬之水了出焉，而東 北流注于【上虍下乎】沱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百里，曰空桑之山，無草木，冬夏有雪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>空桑之水出焉，東流注于【上虍下乎】沱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百里，曰泰戲之山，無草木，多金玉。有獸焉，其狀如羊，一角一目，目在耳 后，其名曰【羊東】【羊東]，其鳴自【□交】。【上虍下乎】沱之水出焉，而東流注于 【樓去木換□】水。液女之水出于其陽，南流注于沁水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百里，曰石山，多藏金玉。囗囗之水出焉，而東流注于【上虍下乎】沱；鮮于之 水出焉，而南流注于【上虍下乎】沱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百里，曰童戎之山。皋塗之水出焉，而東流注于【樓去木換□】液水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百里，曰高是之山。滋水出焉，而南流注于【上虍下乎】沱。其木多棕，其草多 條。【□寇】水出焉，東流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三百里，曰陸山，多美玉。美玉【姜□】水出焉，而東流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北二百里，曰沂山般水出焉，而東流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>北百二十里，曰燕山，多嬰石。燕水出焉，東流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北山行五百里，水行五百里，至于饒山。是無草木，多瑤碧，其獸多囗囗，其鳥多 【留鳥】。歷虢之水出焉，而東流注于河，其中有師魚，食之殺人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北四百里，曰乾山，無草木，其陽有金玉，其陰有鐵而無水。有獸焉，其狀如牛而三 足，其名曰【□原】，其鳴自【□交】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北五百里，曰倫山。倫水出焉，而東流注于河。有獸焉，其狀如麋，其川在尾上，其 名曰羆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北五百里，曰碣石之山。繩水出焉，而東流注于河，其中多蒲夷之魚。基上有玉，其 下多青碧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北水行五百里，至于雁門之山，無草木。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北水行四百里，至于泰澤。其中有山焉，曰帝都之山，廣員百里，無草木，有金玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北五百里，曰【□享】于毋逢之山，北望雞號之山，其風如【左風右三力】。西望幽 都之山，浴水出焉。是有朋蛇，赤首白身，其音如牛，見則其邑大旱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡北次三經之首，自太行之山以至于無逢之山，凡四十六山，萬二千三百五十里。其神 狀皆馬身而人面者廿神。其祠之，皆用一藻【上□下臣】瘞之。其十四神狀皆彘身而載玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>其祠之，皆玉，不瘞。其十神狀皆彘身而八足蛇尾。其祠之，皆用一壁瘞之。大凡四十四 神，皆用【禾余】糈米祠之。此皆不火食。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>右北經之山志，凡八十七山，二萬三千二百三十里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">東山經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">東山經之首，曰【木敕】【上牛左下蟲右下蟲】之山，北臨乾味。食水出焉。而東北流 注于海。其中多□□之魚，其狀如梨牛，其音如彘鳴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰?山，其上有玉，其下有金。湖水出焉，東流注于食水，其中多活師。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰【木旬】狀之山，其上多金玉，其下多青碧石。有獸焉，其狀如犬，六 足，其名曰從從，其鳴自【□交】。有鳥焉，其狀如雞而鼠毛，其名曰【上此下蟲】鼠，見 則其邑大旱。【□只】水出焉。而北流注于湖水。其中多箴魚，其狀如囗，其喙如箴，食之 無疫疾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰勃壘之山，無草木，無水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰番條之山，無草木，多沙。【□咸】水出焉，北流注于海，其中多【魚 感】魚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南四百里，曰姑兒之山，其上多漆，其下多桑柘。姑兒之水出焉，北流注于海，其中 多【魚感】魚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南四百里，曰高氏之山，其上多玉，其下多箴石。諸繩之水出焉，東流注于澤，其中 多金玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰岳山，其上多桑，其下多樗。濼水出焉，東流注于澤，其中多金玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰【□才】山，其上無草木，其下多水，其中多堪【予予】之魚。有獸 焉，其狀如誇父而彘毛，其音如呼，見則天下大水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰獨山，其上多金玉，其下多美石末塗之水出焉，而東流注于沔，其中多 囗【蟲庸】，其狀如黃蛇，魚翼，出入有光，見則其邑大旱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰泰山，其上多玉，其下多金。有獸焉，其狀如豚而有珠，名曰【□同】 【□同】，其鳴自【□交】。環水出焉，東流注于江，其中多水玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰竹山，【□享】于江，無草木，多瑤碧。激水出焉，而東流注于娶檀之 水，其中多茈羸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡東山經之首，自【木敕】【上牛左下蟲右下蟲】之山以至于竹山，凡十二山，三千六 百里。其神狀皆人身龍首。祠：毛用一犬祈，【耳申】用魚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東次二經之首，曰空桑之山，北臨食水，東望沮吳，南望沙陵，西望涮i□右上民右下 日】澤。有獸焉，其狀如牛而虎文，其音如欽。其名曰【車令】【車令】，其鳴自【□ 交】，見則天下大水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南六百里，曰曹夕之山，其下多囗而無木，多鳥獸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西南四百里，曰嶧皋之山，其上多金玉，其下多白堊。嶧皋之水出焉，東流注于激女 之水，其中多蜃珧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南水行五百里，流沙三進里，至于葛山之尾，無草木，多砥礪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百八十里，曰葛山之首，無草木。澧水出焉，東流注于余澤，其中多珠鱉魚，其 狀如囗而有目，六足有珠，其味酸甘，食之無癘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百八十里，曰余【上山下我】之山。其上多梓【左木右丹】，其下多荊杞。雜余 之水出焉，東流注于黃水。有獸焉，其狀如菟而鳥類喙，鴟目蛇尾，見人則眠，名犰狳，其 鳴自【□交】，見則螽蝗為敗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰杜父之山，無草木，多水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰耿山，夫草木，多水碧，多大蛇。有獸焉，其狀如狐而魚翼，其名曰朱 【□需】，其鳴自【□交】見則其國有恐。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰盧其之山，無草木，多沙石，沙水出焉，南流注于涔水，其中多囗鶘， 其狀如鴛鴦而人足，其鳴自【□交】，見則其國多土功。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百八十里，曰姑射之山，無草木，多水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南水行三百里，流沙百里，曰北姑射之山，無草木，多石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰碧山，無草木，多蛇，多碧、多玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南五百里，曰緱氏之山，無草木，多金玉。原水出焉，東流注于沙澤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰姑逢之山，無草木，多金玉。有獸焉，其狀如狐而有翼，其音如鴻雁， 其名曰【□敝】【□敝】，見則天下大旱。、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南五百里，曰鳧麗之山，其上多金玉，其下多箴石，有獸焉，其狀如狐，而九尾、九 首、虎爪，名曰【上龍下蟲】侄，其音如嬰兒，是食人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南五百里，曰【左石右上西右下土】山，南臨【左石右上西右下土】水，東望湖澤， 有獸焉，其狀如馬，而羊目、四角、牛尾，其音如【□皋】狗，其名曰【上山下攸】【上山 下攸】。見則其國多狡客。有鳥焉，其狀如鳧而鼠尾，善登木，其名曰【恝去心換糸】【□ 句】，見則其國多疫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡東次二經之首，自空桑之山至于【左石右上西右下土】山，凡十七山，六千六百四十 里。其神狀皆獸身人面載【角各】。其祠：毛用一雞祈，嬰用一壁瘞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東次三經之首，曰尸胡之山，北望【歹羊】山，其上多金玉，其下多【束束】。有獸 焉，其狀如麋而魚目，名曰囗胡，其鳴自【□交】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南水行八百里，曰岐山，其木多桃李，其獸多虎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南水行七百里，曰諸【□句】之山，無草木，多沙石。是山也，廣員百里，多寐魚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南水行七百里，曰中父之山，無草木，多沙。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東水行千里，曰胡射之山，無草木，多沙石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南水行七百里，曰孟子之山，其木多梓桐，多桃李，其草多菌浦，其獸多麋鹿。是山 也，廣員百里。其上有水出焉，名曰碧陽，其中多囗鮪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南水行五百里，曰流沙，行五百里，有山焉，曰【足支】踵之山，廣員二百里，無草 木，有大蛇，其上多玉。有水焉，廣員四十里皆湧，其名曰深澤，其中多大龜。有魚焉，其 狀如鯉。而六足鳥尾，名曰【魚合】【魚合】之魚，其名自【□交】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南水行九百里，曰【足每】隅之山，其上多草木，多金玉，多赭。有獸焉，其狀如牛 而馬尾，名曰精精，其鳴自【□交】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南水行五百里，流沙三百里，至于無皋之山，南望幼海，東望囗木，無草木，多風。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>是山也，廣員百里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡東次三經之首，自尸胡之山至于無皋之山，凡九山，六千九百里。其神狀皆人身而羊 角。其祠：用一牡羊，米用黍。是神也，見則風雨水為敗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東次四經之首，曰北號之山，臨于北海。有木焉，其狀如楊，赤華，其實如棗而無 核，其味酸甘，食之不瘧。食水出焉，而東北流注于海。有獸焉，其狀如狼，赤首鼠目，其 音如豚，名曰【□曷】狙，是食人。有鳥焉，其狀如雞而白首，鼠足而虎爪，其名曰【鬼 斤】譽亦食人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百里，曰旄山，無草木。蒼體之水出焉，而西浪注于展水，其中多【魚羞】魚， 其狀如鯉而大首，食者不疣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南三百二十里，曰東始之山，上多蒼玉。有木焉，其狀如楊而赤理，其汁如血，不 實，其名曰芑，可以服馬，【□此】水出焉，而東北流注于海，其中多美貝，多茈魚，其狀 如鮒，一首而十身，其臭如囗蕪食之不【米費】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南三百里，曰女丞之山，其上無草木，石膏水出焉，而西流注于鬲水，其中多薄 魚，其狀如囗魚而一目，其音如歐，見則天下大旱。又東南二百里，曰欽山，多金玉而無 石。師水出焉，而北流注于皋澤，其中多【魚羞】魚，多文貝。有獸焉，其狀如豚而有牙， 其名曰當康，其鳴自【□交】，見則天下大穰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南二百里，曰子桐之山。子桐之水出焉，而西流注于余如之澤。其中多【魚骨】 魚，其狀如魚而鳥翼，出入有光。其音如鴛鴦，見則天下大旱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北二百里，曰剡山，多金玉。有獸焉，其狀如彘而人面。黃身而赤尾，其名曰合 囗，其音如嬰兒，是獸也，食人，亦食蟲蛇，見則天下大水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北二百里，曰太山，上多金玉楨木。有獸焉，其狀如【牛而】白首，一目而蛇尾， 其名曰蜚，行水則竭，行草則死，見則天下大疫，【□句】水出焉，而北流注于勞水，其中 的【魚羞】魚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡東次四經之首，自北號之山至于太山，凡八山，一千七百二十里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">中山經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">中山經薄山之首，曰甘棗之山，共水出焉，而西流注于河。其上多??木。其下有草焉， 葵本而可葉。黃華而莢實，名曰籜，可以已懵。有獸焉，其狀如囗鼠而文題，其名曰【左上 革左下夫右能】，食之已癭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二十里，曰歷兒之山，其上多囗，多【木萬】木，是木也，方莖而員葉，黃華而 毛，其實如揀，服之不忘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東十五里，曰渠豬之山，其上多竹，渠豬之水出焉，而南流注于河。其中是多豪魚， 狀如【魚有】，赤喙尾赤羽，可以已白癬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三十五里，曰蔥聾之山，其中多大谷，是多白堊，黑、青、黃堊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東十五里，曰【□委】山，其上多赤銅，其陰多鐵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東七十里，曰脫扈之山。有草焉，其狀如葵葉而赤華，莢實，實如棕莢，名曰植褚， 可以已【□鼠】，食之不瞇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二十里，曰金星之山，多天嬰，其狀如龍骨，可以已痤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東七十里，曰泰威之山。其中有谷，曰梟谷，其中多鐵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東十五里，曰囗谷之山。其中多赤銅。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東百二十里，曰吳林之山，其中多囗草。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三十里，曰牛首之山。有草焉，名曰鬼草，其葉如葵而赤莖，其秀如禾，服之不 憂。勞水出焉，而西流注于囗水，是多飛魚，其狀如鮒魚，食之已痔【彳同亍】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北四十里，曰霍山，其木多楮。有獸焉，其狀如狸，而白尾有鬣，名曰【月出】【月 出】，養之可以已憂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北五十二里，曰合谷之山，是多【上□下詹】棘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三十五里，曰陰山，多礪石、文石。少水出焉，其中多雕棠，其葉如榆葉而方，其 實如赤菽，食之已聾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北四百里，曰鼓鐙之山，多赤銅。有草焉，名曰榮草，其葉如柳，其本如雞卵，莨 之已風。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡薄山之首，白甘棗之山至于鼓鐙之山，凡十五山，六千六百七十里。歷兒、塚也，其 祠禮：毛，太牢之具，縣以吉玉。其余十三者，毛用一羊，縣嬰用桑封，瘞而不糈。桑封 者，桑主也，方其下而銳其上，而中穿之加金。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>中次二經注山之首，曰【火軍】諸之山，其上多桑，其獸多閭麋，其鳥多【曷鳥】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西南二百里，曰發視之山，其上多金玉，其下多砥礪。即魚之水出焉，而西流注于伊 水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百里，曰豪山，其上多金玉而無草木。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百里，曰鮮山，多金玉，無草木，鮮水出焉，而北流注于伊水。其中多鳴蛇，其 狀如蛇而四翼，其音如磬，見則其邑大旱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百里，曰陽山，多石，無草木。陽水出焉，而北流注于伊水。其中多化蛇，其狀 如人面而豺身，鳥翼而蛇行，其音如叱呼，見其邑大水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百里，曰昆吾之山，其上多赤銅。有獸焉，其狀如彘而有角，其音如號，名曰 【上龍下蟲】【蟲氏】，食之不瞇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西百二十里，曰荔山。荔水出焉，而北流注于伊水，其上多金玉，其下多青雄黃。有 木焉，其狀如棠而赤時，名曰芒草，可以毒魚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西一百五十里，曰蔓渠之山，其上多金玉，其下多竹箭。伊水出焉，而東流注于洛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有獸焉，其名曰馬腹，其狀如人面虎身，其音如嬰兒，是食人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡濟山之首，自【火軍】諸之山至于蔓渠之山，凡九山，一千六百七十里，其神皆人面 而鳥身。祠用毛，用一吉玉，投而不糈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>中次三以【上□下負】山之首，曰敖岸之山，其陽多【王雩】【王孚】之玉，其陰多 赭、黃金。神熏池居之。是常出美玉。北望河林，其狀如茜如舉。有獸焉，其狀如白鹿而四 角，名曰夫諸，見則其邑大水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東十里，曰青要之山，實惟帝之密都。北望河曲，是多駕鳥。南望【土單】渚，禹父 之所化，中多僕累、蒲盧。【鬼申】武羅司之，其狀人面而豹文，小要而白齒，而穿耳以 囗，其鳴如鳴玉。是山也，宜女子。畛水出焉，而北流注于河。其中有鳥焉，名曰【幼 鳥】，其狀如鳧，青身而朱目赤尾，食之宜子。?有草焉，其狀如囗，而方莖黃華赤實，其 本如□木，名曰荀草，服之美人色。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東十里，曰【馬鬼】山，其上有美棗，其陰有【王雩】【王孚】之玉。正回之水出 焉，而北流注于河。其中多飛魚，其狀如豚而赤文，服之不畏雷，可以御兵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東四十里，曰宜蘇之山，其上多金玉，其下多蔓居之木。【□庸】【□庸】之水出 焉，而北流注于河，是多黃貝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二十里，曰和山，其上無草木而多瑤碧，實惟河之九都。是山也五曲，九水出焉， 合而北流注于河，其中多蒼玉。吉神泰逢司之，其狀如人而虎尾，是好居于【上□下負】山 之陽，出入有光。泰逢神動天地氣也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡【上□下負】之首，自敖岸之山至于和山，凡五山，四百四十里。其祠：泰逢、熏 池、武羅皆一牡羊副，嬰用吉玉。其二神用一雄雞瘞之。糈用【禾余】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>中次四經厘山之首，曰鹿蹄之山，其上多玉，其下多金。甘水出下，而北流注于洛，其 中多泠石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西五十里，曰扶豬之山，其上多【石需】石。有獸焉，其狀如貉而人目，其名曰【上鹿 下言】。虢水出焉，而北流注于洛，其中多【石需】石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西一百二十里，曰厘山，其陽多玉，其陰多【上□下鬼】。有獸焉，其狀如牛。蒼 身，其音如嬰兒，是食人，其名曰犀渠。【□庸】【□庸】之水出 又西一百二十里，曰厘山，其陽多玉，其陰多【上□下鬼】。有獸焉，其狀如牛。蒼 身，其音如嬰兒，是食人，其名曰犀渠。【□庸】【□庸】之水出焉，而南流注于伊水。有 獸焉，名曰【□吉頁】，其狀如□犬而有鱗，其毛如彘鬣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百里，曰箕尾之山，多楮，多塗石，其上多【王雩】【王孚】之玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百里，曰箕尾之山，基個多玉，其下多銅。滔雕之水出焉，而北流注于洛。其中 多【羊咸】羊。有木焉，其狀如樗，其葉如桐而莢實，其名曰茇，可以毒魚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百里，曰白邊之山，其上多金玉，其下多青雄黃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二百里，曰熊耳之山，其上多漆，其下多棕。浮濠之水出焉，而西流注于洛，其中 多水玉，多人魚。有草焉，其狀如蘇而赤華，名曰葶苧，可以毒魚。又西三百里，曰牡山， 其上多文石，其下多竹箭竹【上竹下媚】，其獸多【牛乍】牛、【羊咸】羊，鳥多赤【上敝 下鳥】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三百五十里，曰囗舉之山。雒水出焉，而東北流注于玄扈之水，其中多腸之物。此 二山者，洛間也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡厘冊之首，自鹿蹄之山至于玄扈之山，凡九山，千六百里七十里。其神狀皆人面獸 身。其祠之，毛用一白雞，祈而不糈，以採衣之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>中次五經薄山之苟，曰苟床之山，無草木，多怪石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東三百里，曰首山，其陰多楮柞，其草多【上□下術】芫，其陽多【王雩】【王孚】之 玉，木多槐。其陰有谷，曰機谷，多【鳥大】鳥，其狀如錄，食之已墊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百里，曰縣【屬斤】之山，無草木，多文石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百里，曰蔥聾之山，無草木，多囗石。東北五百里，曰條谷之山，其木多槐桐， 其草多芍藥、門冬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北十里，曰超山，其陰多蒼玉，其陽有井，冬有水而夏竭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東十里，曰成侯之山，其上多【木熏】木，其草多【上□下凡】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰朝歌之山，谷多美堊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰隗山，谷多金錫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東十里，曰歷山，其木多槐，其陽多玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東十里，曰尸山，多蒼玉，其獸多【上鹿下京】。尸水出焉，南流注于洛水，其中多 美玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東十里，曰良余之山，基上多楮柞，無石。余水出于其陰，而北流注于河；乳水出于 其陽，而東南流注于洛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南十里，曰蠱尾之山，多礪石、赤銅。龍余之水出焉，而東南流注于洛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北二十里，曰升山，其木其多楮柞棘，其草多【上□下諸】蕙，多寇脫。黃酸之水 出焉，而北流注于河，其中多璇玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二十里，曰陽虛之山，多金，臨于玄扈之水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡薄山之首，自苟林之山至于陽虛之山，凡十六山，二千九百八十二里。升山，塚也， 其祠禮：太牢，嬰用吉玉。首山，【鬼申】也，其祠用【禾余】、黑犧太牢之具、□釀；幹 ?，置鼓；嬰用一璧。尸水，合天也，肥牲祠也；用一黑犬于上，用一雌雞于下，刮一牝 羊，獻血。嬰用吉玉，採之，饗之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>中次六經縞【羊氐】山之首，曰平逢之山，南望伊洛，東望谷城之山，無草木，無水， 多沙石。有神焉，其狀如人而二首，名曰驕蟲，是為螫蟲，實惟蜂蜜之廬，其祠之，用一雄 雞，禳而勿殺。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西十里，曰縞【羊氐】之山，無草木，多金玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西十里，曰【外□內鬼】山，其陰多【王雩】【王孚】之玉。其西有谷焉，名曰帙 谷，其木多柳楮。其中有鳥焉，狀如山雞而長尾，赤如丹火而青喙，名曰【令鳥】【要 鳥】，其鳴自呼，服之不瞇。交觴之水出于陽，而南流于洛；俞隨之水出于其陰，而北流注 于谷水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三十里，曰瞻諸之山，其陽多金，其陰多文石。謝水出焉，而東南流注于洛，少水 出其陰，而北流注于谷水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三十里，曰婁豕之山，無草木，多金玉。瞻水出于其陽，而東流注于洛；陂水出于 其陰，而北流注于谷水其中多茈石、文石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西四十里，曰白石之山，惠水出于其陽，而南流注于洛，其中多水玉，澗水出于其陰 西北流注于谷水，其中多麋石、櫨丹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西五十里，曰谷山，其上多楮，其下多桑。爽水出焉，而西北流注于谷水，其中多碧 綠。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西七十二里，曰密山，其陰多玉，基陰多鐵。豪水出焉，而南流注于洛，其中多旋 龜，其狀鳥首而鱉尾，其音如判木。無草木。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西百里，曰長石之山，無草木，多鑫玉。其西有谷焉，名曰共谷，多竹。共水出焉， 西南流注于洛，其中多鳴石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西一百四十里，曰傅山，無草木，多瑤碧。厭染之水出于其陽，而南流注于洛，其中 多人魚。其西有林焉。名曰?塚，谷水出焉，而東流注于洛其中多【王因】玉。 又西五十里，曰橐山，其木多樗，多囗木，其陽多金玉，其陰多鐵，多蕭。橐水出焉， 而北流注于河。其中多修闢之魚，狀如黽而白喙，其音如鴟，食之已白癬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西九十里，日常【上丞下□】之山，無草木，多堊，【□焦】水出焉，而東北流注于 河，其中多蒼玉。【上□下甾】水出焉，而北流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西九十里，曰誇父之山，其木多棕【木丹】，多竹箭，其獸多【牛乍】牛、【羊咸】 羊，其鳥多【上敝下鳥】，其陽多玉，其陰多鐵。其北有林焉，名曰桃林，是廣員三百里， 其中多馬。湖水出焉，而北流注于河，其中多【王因】玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西九十里，曰陽華之山，其陽多金玉，其陰多青雄黃，其草多【上□下諸】囗，多苦 辛，其狀如【木肅】，其實如瓜，其味酸甘，食之已瘧。楊水出焉，而西南流注于洛，其中 多人魚。門水出焉，而東北流注于河，其中多玄【石肅】。【□昔】姑之水出于其陰，而東 流注于門水，其上多銅牆鐵壁。門水出于河，七百九十里入【名隹】水。凡縞【羊氐】山之 首，自平逢之山至于陽華之山，凡十四山，七百九十里。岳在其中，以六月祭之，如諸岳之 祠法，則天下安寧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>中次七經苦山之首，曰休囗之山。其上有石焉，名曰帝台之棋，五色而文其狀如鶉卵， 帝台之石，所以禱百神者也，服之不蠱。有草焉，其狀如蓍，赤葉而本生。名曰夙條，可以 為囗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東三百里，曰鼓鐘之山，帝台之所以觴百神也。有草焉，方莖而黃華，員葉擊三成，其 名曰焉酸，可以為毒。其上多礪，其下多礪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二百里，曰姑囗之山。帝女死焉，其名曰女尸，化為囗草，其葉胥成，其華黃，其 這關如菟丘，服之媚于人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二十里，曰苦山，有獸焉，名曰黃棘，黃華而不實，名曰無條，服之不字。有草 焉，員葉而無莖，赤華而不實，名曰無條，服之不癭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二十七里，曰堵山，神天愚居之，是多怪風雨，其上有木焉，名曰天【木扁】，方 莖而葵狀，服者不【左口右上西右下土】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五十二里，曰放皋之山。明水出焉。南流注于伊水，其中多蒼玉。有木焉，其葉如 蜂，枝尾而反舌，善呼，其名曰文文。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五十七里，曰大【上非下古】之山，多【王雩】【王孚】之玉，多麋玉。有草焉， 其狀如榆，方莖而蒼傷，其名曰牛傷，其根蒼文，服者為厥，可以御兵。其陽狂水出焉，西 南流注于伊水，其中多三足龜，食者無大疾，可以已腫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東七十里，曰半石之山。其上有草焉，生而秀，其高丈余</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>曰嘉榮，服之者不霆。米需之水出于其陽，西流注于伊水，其中多【魚崙】魚，黑文，其狀 如鮒，食得不睡。合水出于其陰，而北流注于洛，多【左月右上關右下魚】魚，狀如鱖，居 逵，蒼文赤尾，食者不癰，可以為□。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五十里，曰少室之山，百草木成a。葉其上有木器焉，各曰帝 五衢，黃華黑實，服者不怒。其上多玉，其下多鐵。休水出焉，而北流注于洛，其中多 【魚帝】魚，狀如囗【蟲隹】而長距，足白而對，食者無蠱疾，可以御兵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三十里，曰泰室之山。其上有木焉，葉狀如梨而赤理，其名曰【木有】木，服者不 妒。有草焉，其狀如【上□下術】，白華黑實，澤如【上□下嬰】【上□下奧】，其名曰囗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>草，服之不味。上多美石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三十里，曰講山，其上多玉，多柘，多柏。有木焉，名曰帝屋，葉狀如椒，反傷赤 實，可以御凶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又北三十里，曰嬰梁之山，上多蒼玉，【□享】于玄石。又東三十里，曰浮戲之山。有 木焉，葉狀如【木雩】而赤實，名曰亢木，食之不蠱，汜水出焉，而北流注于河。其東有 谷，因名曰蛇谷，上多少辛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東四十里，曰少陘之山。有草焉，名曰【上□下岡】草，葉狀如葵，而赤莖白華，實 如【上□下嬰】【上□下奧】，食之不愚。器難之水出焉，而北流注于役水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南十里，曰太山。有草焉，名曰梨，其葉狀如囗而赤華，可以已疽主水出于其陽， 而東流注于役。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二十里，曰末山，上多赤金，末水出焉，北流注于役。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二十五里，曰役山，上多白金，多鐵。役水出焉，北流注于河。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三十五里，曰敏山。上有木焉，其狀如荊，白華而赤實，名曰薊柏，服者不寒其陽 多【王雩】【王孚】之玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三十里，曰大【馬鬼】之山，其陰多鐵、美玉、青堊。有草焉，其狀如蓍而毛，青 華而不實，其名曰【上□下狼】，服之不夭，可以為腹病。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡苦山這首，自休輿之山至于大【馬鬼】之山，凡十有九山，千一百八十四里。其十六 神者，皆豕身而人面。其祠：毛【牛全】用一羊羞，嬰用一藻玉瘞。苦山、少室、太室皆塚 也，其祠之，太牢之具，嬰以吉玉。其神狀皆人面而三首。其余屬皆豕身而人面也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>中次八經荊山之首，曰景山，其上多金玉，其木多杼檀。睢水出焉，東南流注于江，其 中多丹粟，多文魚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東北百里，曰荊山，其陰多鐵，其陽多赤金，其中多【左上未右上□中廠下牛】牛，多 豹虎，其木多松柏，其草多竹，多橘【木繇】。漳水出焉，而東南流注于睢，其中多黃金， 多鮫魚，其獸多閭麋。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北百五十里，曰驕山，其上多玉，其下多青【鑊□換丹】，其木多松柏，多桃枝鉤 端。神【上單左下蟲右下蟲】圍處之，其狀如人面。羊角虎爪，恆游于睢漳之淵，出入有光。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北百二十里，曰女幾之山，其上多玉，其下多黃金，其獸多豹虎，多閭麋【上鹿下 京】麂，其鳥多白【喬鳥】，多翟，多鴆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北二百里，曰宜諸之山，其上多金玉，其下多青【鑊□換丹】。【□危】水出焉， 而南流注于漳，其中多白玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北三百五十里，曰綸山，其木多梓【木丹】，多桃枝，多【木且】粟橘【木繇】，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>其痼多閭麂囗【上召中比下大】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北二百里，曰陸【危□】之山，其上多【王雩】【王孚】之玉，其下多堊，其木多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>?【左木加疆右邊】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東百三十里，曰光山，其上多碧，其下多木。神計蒙處之，其狀人身而龍首，恆游于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>漳淵，出入必有飄風暴雨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北百五十里，曰岐山，其陽多赤金，其陰多白□，其上多金玉，其下多青【鑊□換</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>丹】，其林多【木雩】。神涉【上單左下蟲右下蟲】處之，其狀人身而方面三足。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東百三十里，曰銅山，其上多金銀鐵，其木多楮柞?粟橘囗，其獸多【矛勺】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北一百里，曰美山，其獸多野牛，多閭【上鹿下主】，多豕鹿，其上多金，其下多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>青【左丹右上萑右下又】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北百里，曰大堯之山，其木多松柏，多梓桑，多機，其草多竹，其獸多豹虎囗【上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>召中比下大】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北三百里，曰靈山，其上多金玉，其下多青【鑊□換丹】，其木多桃李梅杏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北七十里，曰龍山，上多寓木，其木多碧，其下多赤錫，其草多桃枝鉤端。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南五十里，曰衡山，上多寓木楮柞，多黃堊白堊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南七十里，曰石山，其上多金，其下多青【鑊□換丹】，多寓木。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南百二十里，曰若山，其上多【王雩】【王孚】玉，多赭，多【圭□】石，多寓木，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>多柘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><h5>又東南一百二十里，曰彘山，多美石，多柘C</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南一百五十里，曰玉山，其上多金玉，其下多碧、鐵，其木多柏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南七十里，曰灌山，其木多檀，多【圭□】石，多白錫。鬱水出于其上，潛于其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>下，其中多砥礪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北百五十里，曰仁舉之山，其木多楮柞，其陽多赤金，其陰多赭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五十里，曰師每之山，其陽多砥礪，其陰多青【鑊□換丹】，其木多柏，多檀，多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>柘，其草多竹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南二百里，曰琴鼓之山，其木多楮柞椒柘，其上多白□，其下多洗石，其獸多豕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>鹿，多白犀，其鳥多鴆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡荊山之首，自景山至琴鼓之山，凡二十三山，二千八百九十里。其神狀皆鳥身而人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>面。其祠：用一雄雞祈瘞，用一藻圭，糈用【禾余】。驕山，塚也，其祠：用羞酒少牢祈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>瘞，嬰毛一璧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>中次九經岷山之首，曰女幾之山，其上多石涅，其木多?【疆左邊換木】，其草多菊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【上□下術】。洛水出焉，東注于江，其中多雄黃，其獸多虎豹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北三百里，曰岷山。江水出焉，東北流注于海，其中多良龜，多【上魚下黽】，其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>上多金玉，其下多白□，其木多梅棠，其獸多犀象，多夔牛，其鳥多翰、【上敝下鳥】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北一百四十里，曰崍山。江水出焉，東流注于江。其陽多黃金，其陰多麋【上鹿下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>主】，其木多檀柘，其草多囗韭，多藥、空奪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東一百五十里，曰【山居】山。江水出焉，東流注于大江，其中多怪蛇，多囗魚，其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>木多【木猷】?，多梅梓，其獸多夔牛、囗、【上召中比下大】、犀、兕。有鳥焉，狀如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【號鳥】而赤身白首，其名曰竊脂，可以御火。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百里，曰高梁之山，其上多堊，其下多砥礪，其木多桃枝鉤端。有草焉，狀如葵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>而赤華、莢實、白【木付】，可以走馬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東四百里，曰蛇山，其上多黃金，其下多堊，其木多【木旬】，多豫章，其草多嘉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>榮、少辛。有獸焉，其狀如狐，而白尾長耳，名【□也】狼，見則國內有兵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五百里，曰鬲山，其陽多金，其陰多白□。蒲囗之水出焉，而東流注于江，其中多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>白玉，其獸多犀象熊羆，多【□爰】【蟲隹】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北三百里，曰隅陽之山，其上多金玉，其下多青【鑊□換丹】，其木多梓桑，其草</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>多茈。徐水出焉，東流注于江，其中多丹粟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二百五十里，曰岐山，其上多白金，其下多鐵。其木多梅梓，多?【木酋】。【□</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>咸】水出焉，東南流注于江。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百里，曰勾【木爾】之山，其上多玉，其下多黃金，其木多櫟柘，其草多芍藥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東一百五十里，曰風雨之山，其上多白金，其下多石涅，其木多【木取】【木單】，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>多楊。宣余之水出焉，東流注于江，其中多蛇，其獸多閭麋，多【上鹿下主】豹虎，其鳥多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>白【喬鳥】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北二百里，曰玉山，其陽多銅，其陰多赤金，其木多豫章、囗、?，其獸多豕鹿囗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【上召中比下大】，其鳥多鴆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東一百五十里，曰熊山。有空焉，熊之空，恆出神人。夏啟而冬閉，是穴也，冬啟乃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>必有兵。其上多白玉，其下多白金。其林多樗柳，其草多寇脫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東一百四十里，曰【馬鬼】山，其陽多美玉赤金，其陰多鐵，其木金桃枝荊芭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二百里，曰葛山，其上多赤金，其下多【王咸】石，其木多【木且】慄橘【木繇】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【木酋】?，其獸多囗【上召中比下大】，其草多嘉榮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東一百七十里，曰賈超之山，其陽多黃堊，其陰多美赭，其木【木且】慄橘【木繇】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【木酋】?，其中多美修。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡岷山之首，自女幾山至于賈超之山，凡十六山，三千五百里。其神狀皆馬身而龍首。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>其祠：毛用一雄雞瘞。糈用【禾余】。文山、勾【木爾】、風雨、【馬鬼】之山，是皆塚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>也，其祠之：羞酒，少牢具，嬰毛一吉玉。熊山，席也，其祠：羞酒，太牢具，嬰毛一璧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>幹?，用兵以禳；祈，【王加戮左邊】冕舞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>中次經十經之首，曰首陽之山，其上多金玉，無草木。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西五十里，曰虎尾之山，其木多椒椐，多封石，其陽多赤金，其陰多鐵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西南五十里，曰繁繢之山，其木多【木酋】?，其草多枝勾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西南二十里，曰勇石之山，無草木，多白金，多木</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二十里，曰複州之山，其木多檀，其陽多黃金。有鳥焉，其狀如【號鳥】，而一足</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>彘尾，其名曰【足支】踵，見則其國大疫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西三十里，曰楮山，多寓木，多椒椐，多柘，多堊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西二十里，曰又原之山，其陽多青【左丹右上萑右下又】，其陰多鐵，其鳥多【瞿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>鳥】鵒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西五十里，曰涿山，其木多谷柞?，其陽多【王雩】【王孚】之玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西七十里，曰丙山，其木多梓檀，多【弓欠】?。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><h5>凡首陽山之滿A自首山至于丙山，凡九山，二百六十七里。其神狀皆龍身而人面。其祠</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>之：毛用一雄雞瘞，糈用五種之糈。堵山，塚也，其祠之：少牢具，羞祠，嬰毛一璧。【馬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>鬼】山，帝也，其祠羞酒，太牢其巫祝二人?，嬰一璧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>中次一十一山經荊山之首，曰翼望之山。湍水出焉，東流注于濟；見兄水出焉，東南流</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>注于漢，其中多蛟。其上多松柏，其下多漆梓，其陽多赤金，其陰多□。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北一百五十里，曰朝歌之山，【□無】水出焉，東南流注于滎，其中多人魚。其上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>多梓【木丹】，其獸多【上鹿中雨下三口】麋。有草焉，名曰莽草，可以毒魚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南二百里，曰帝^□劍□溲舳唷就貊□俊就躡□恐□瘢□湟醵□□□帝^□□□</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>諂瀋希□庇諂湎攏□嗝□摺□</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南五十里，曰視山，其上多韭。有井焉，名曰天井，夏有水，冬竭。其上多桑，多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>美堊金玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南二百里，曰前山，其木多櫧，多柏，其陽多金，其陰多赭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南三百里，曰豐山。有獸焉，其狀如【蟲爰】，赤目，赤喙，黃身，名曰雍和，見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>則國有大恐。神耕父處之，常游清泠之淵，出入有光，見則其國為敗。有九鐘焉，是知霜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>鳴。其上多金，其下多金，其下多谷柞?囗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北八百里，曰兔床之山，其陽多鐵，其木多【上□下諸】囗其草多雞谷，其本如雞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>卵，其味酸甘，食者利于人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東六十里，曰皮山，多堊，多赭，其木多松柏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東六十里，曰瑤碧之山，其木多梓【木丹】，其陰多青【鑊□換丹】，其陽多白金。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有鳥焉，其狀如雉，恆食蜚，名曰鴆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東四十里，曰支離之山。濟水出焉，南流注于漢。有鳥焉，其名曰嬰勺，其狀如鵲，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>赤目、赤喙、白身，其尾若勺，共鳴自呼。多【牛乍】牛，多【羊咸】羊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北五十里，曰帙【上竹下周】之山，其上多松柏機柏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又西北一百里，曰堇理之山，其上多松柏，多美梓，其陰多丹【鑊□換丹】，多金，其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>獸多豹虎。有鳥焉，其狀如鵲，青身白喙，白目白尾，名曰青耕，可以御疫，其鳴自叫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南三十里，曰依□之山，其上多?囗，多苴。有獸焉，其狀如犬，虎爪有甲，其名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>曰【麟鹿換□】，善【馬央】【上分下牛】，食者不風。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南三十五里，曰即谷之山，多美玉，多玄豹，多閭【上鹿下主】，多【上鹿中雨下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>三口】【上召中比下大】。其陰多□，其陰多青【鑊□換丹】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南四十里，曰雞山，其上多美梓，多桑，其草多韭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南五十里，曰高前之山，其上有水焉，甚寒而清，帝台之漿也，飲之者不心痛。其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>上有金，其下有赭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南三十里，曰游戲之山，多?【殭□換木】谷，多玉，多封石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南三十五里，曰從山，其上多松柏，其下多竹。從水出于其上，潛于其下，其中多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>三足鱉，枝尾，食之無蠱疫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南三十里，曰嬰【左石右上西右下土】，其上多松柏，其下多梓【木熏】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南三十里，曰畢山。帝苑之水出焉，東北流注于視，其中多水玉，多蛟。其上多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【王雩】【王孚】之玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南二十里，曰樂馬之山。有獸焉，其狀如囗【音匯，蝟的意思】，赤如丹火，其名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>曰【□戾】，見則其國大疫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南二十五里，曰【上□下咸】山，視水出焉，東南流注于汝水，其中多人魚，多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>蛟，多頡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東四十里，曰嬰山，其下多青【鑊□換丹】，其上多金玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三十里，曰虎首之山，多苴【木周】椐。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二十里，曰嬰侯之山，其上多封石，其下多赤錫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五十里，曰大孰之山。殺水出焉，東北流注于視水，其中多白堊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><h5>又東四十里，曰卑山，其上多桃李苴梓，多【4鞢熨漇T□</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三十里，曰倚帝之山，其上多玉，其下多金。有獸焉，狀如【鼠犬】鼠，白耳白</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>喙，名曰狙如，見則其國有大兵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三十里，曰鯢山，鯢水出于其上，潛于其下，其中多美堊。其上多金，其下多青</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【鑊□換丹】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三十里，曰雅山。澧水出焉，東流注于視水，其中有大魚。其上多美桑，其下多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>苴，多赤金。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五十五里，曰宣山。淪水出焉，東南流注于視水，其中多蛟。其上有桑焉，大五十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>尺，其枝四衢，其葉大尺余，赤理黃華青【木付】，名曰帝女之桑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東四十五里，曰衡山，其上多青【鑊□換丹】，多桑，其鳥多【瞿鳥】鵒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東四十里，曰豐山，其上多封石，其木多桑，多羊桃，狀如桃而方莖，可以為皮張。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東七十里，曰嫗山，其上多美玉，其下多金，其草多雞谷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三十里，曰鮮山，其木多【木酋】?苴，其草多萱冬，其陽多金，其陰多鐵。有獸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>焉，其狀如膜大，赤喙、赤目、白尾，見則其邑有火，名曰【□多】即。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三十里，曰章山，其陽多美玉。皋水出焉，東流注于澧水，其中多【月色】石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二十五里，曰大支之山，其陽多金，其木多谷柞，無草木。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五十里，曰區吳之山，其木多苴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五十里，曰聲匈之山，其木多楮，多玉，上多封石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東五十里，曰大【馬鬼】之山，其陽多赤金，其陰多砥石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東十里，曰踵搕坐s，無草木。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東北七十里，曰歷石之山，其木多荊芑，其陽多黃金。其陰多砥石。有獸焉，其狀如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>狸，而白首虎爪，名曰梁渠，見則其國有大兵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南一百里，曰求山。求水出于其上，潛于其下，中有美赭。其木多苴，多【上竹下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>媚】。其陽多金，其陰多鐵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二百里，曰醜陽之山，其上多【木周】椐。有鳥焉，其狀如烏而赤足，名曰【鳥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>只】【鳥余】，可以御火。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百里，曰奧山，其上多柏?【殭□換木】，其陽多【王雩】【王孚】之玉。奧水</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>出焉，東流注于視水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三十五里，曰服山，其木多苴，其上多封石，其下多赤錫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東百十里，曰杳山，其上多嘉榮草，多金玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東三百五十里，曰幾山，其木多【木酋】【殭□換木】?，其草多香。有獸焉，其狀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>如彘，黃身、白頭、白尾，名曰聞【麟鹿換□】，見則天下大風。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡荊山之首，自翼望之山至于幾山，凡四十八山，三千七百三十二里。其神狀皆彘身人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>首。其祠：毛用一雄雞祈瘞，用一【王圭】，糈用五種之精。禾山，帝也，其祠：太牢之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>具，羞瘞，倒毛；用一璧，牛無常。堵山、玉山，塚也，皆倒祠，羞毛少牢，嬰毛吉玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>中次十二經洞庭山首，曰篇遇之山，無草木，多黃金。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南五十里，曰云山，無草木。有桂竹，甚毒，傷人必死，其上多黃金，其下多【王</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>雩】【王孚】之玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南一百三十里，曰龜山，其木多谷柞【木周】椐，其上多黃金，其下多青雄黃，多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>扶竹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東七十里，曰丙山，多【上竹下圭】竹，多黃金銅鐵，無木。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南五十里，曰鳳伯之山，其上多金玉，其下多囗石文石，多鐵，其木多柳?、檀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>楮。其東有林焉，曰莽浮之林，美木鳥獸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東一百五十里，曰夫夫之山，其上多黃金，其下多青雄黃，其木多桑楮，其草多竹、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>雞鼓。神于兒居之，其狀人身而身操兩蛇，常游于江淵，出入有光。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南一百十里，曰洞庭之山，其上多黃金，其下多銀鐵，其木多【木且】梨橘【木</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>繇】，其草多囗【音間，蘭草古稱】、【上□下麋】蕪、芍藥、芎【上□下窮】。帝之二女</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>居之，是常游于江淵。澧沅之風，交瀟湘之淵，是在九江之間，出入必以飄風暴雨，是多怪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>神，狀如人而載蛇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南一百八十里，曰暴山，其木多棕【木丹】荊芑竹箭【上竹下媚】菌，其上多黃金</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>玉，其下多文石鐵，其獸多麋鹿【上鹿下旨】就。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南二百里，曰即公之山，其上多黃金，其下多【王雩】【王孚】之玉，其鴞h柳?</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>檀桑。有獸焉，其狀如龜，而白身赤首，名曰蓐，是可以御火。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南一百五十里，曰堯山，其陰多黃堊，其陽多黃金，其木多荊芑柳檀，其草多【上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>□下諸】囗【上□下術】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南一百里，曰江浮之山，其上多銀砥礪，無草木，其獸多豕鹿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東二百里，曰真陵之山，其上多黃金，其下多玉，其木多谷柞柳?，其草多榮草。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又東南一百二十里，曰陽帝之山，多美銅，其木多【殭□換木】?楮，其獸多【上鹿中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>雨下三口】麝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又南九十里，曰柴桑之山，其上多銀，其下多碧，多泠石赭，其木多芑，其蟲多怪蛇怪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>蟲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>凡洞庭山之首，自篇遇之山至于榮余之山，凡十萬山，二千八百里。其神狀皆鳥身而龍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>首。其祠：毛用一雄雞、一牝豚刮，糈用【禾余】。凡夫夫之山、即公之山，堯山、陽帝之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>山皆塚也，其祠：皆肆瘞，祈用酒，毛用少牢，嬰毛一吉玉。洞庭、榮余山神也，其祠：皆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>肆瘞，祈酒太牢祠，嬰用圭璧十五，五採惠之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>右中經之山志，大凡百九十七山，二萬一千三百七十一里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大凡天下名山五千三百七十，居地，大凡六萬四千五十六里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>禹曰：天下名山，經五千三百七十山，六萬四千五十六里，居地也。言其《五臧》，蓋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>其余小山甚眾，不足記云。天地之東西二萬八千里，南北二萬六千里，出水之山者八千里，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>受水者八千里，出銅之山四百六十七，出鐵之山三千六百九十。此在地之m所分壤樹谷也，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>戈矛之所發也，刀鎩之所起也，能者有余，拙者不足。封于太山，禪于梁父，七十二家，得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>失之數，皆在此內，是謂國用。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>右《五臧山經》五篇，大凡一萬五千五百三字。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海外南經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">地之所載，六合之間，四海之內，照之以日月，經之以星辰，紀之以四時，要之以太</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>歲，神靈所生，其物異形，或天或壽，唯聖人能通其道。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>海外自西南陬至東南陬者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>結匈國在其西南，其為人結匈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>南山在其東南。自此山來，蟲為蛇，蛇號為魚。一曰南山在結匈東南。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>比翼鳥在其東，其為鳥青、赤，兩鳥比翼。一曰在南山東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>羽民國在其東南，其為人長，身生羽。一曰在比翼鳥東南，其為人長頰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有神人二八，連臂，為帝司夜于此野。在羽民東。其為小人頰赤肩。盡十六人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>畢方鳥在其東，青水西，其為鳥人面一腳。一曰在二八神東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【灌□換□】頭國在其南，其為人人面有翼，鳥喙，方捕魚。一曰在畢方東。或曰【灌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>□換□】朱國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>厭火國在其國南，獸身黑色。生火出其口中。一曰在【灌□換□】朱東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>三株樹在厭火北，生赤水上，其為樹如柏，葉皆為珠。一曰其為樹若彗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>三苗國在赤水東，其為人相隨。一曰三毛國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【載車換至】國在其東，其為人黃，能操弓射蛇。一曰【載車換至】國在三毛東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>貫匈國在其東，其為人匈有竅。一曰在【載車換至】國東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>交脛國在其東，其為大交脛。一曰在穿匈東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>不死民在其東，其為人黑色，壽，不死。一曰在穿匈國東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>歧舌國在其東。一曰在不死民東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>昆崙虛在其東，虛四方。一曰在歧舌東，為虛四方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>羿與鑿齒戰于壽華之野，羿射殺之。在昆崙虛東。羿持弓矢，鑿齒持盾。一曰戈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>三首國在其東，其為人一身三首。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>周饒國在東，其為人短小，冠帶。一曰周饒國在三首東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>長臂國在其東，捕魚水中，兩手保操一魚。一曰在周饒東，捕魚海中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>狄山，帝堯葬于陽，帝嚳葬于陰。爰有熊、羆、文虎、【蟲隹】、豹、離朱、視肉；籲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>咽、文王皆葬其所。一曰湯山。一曰爰有熊、羆、文虎、【蟲隹】、豹、離朱、【丘鳥】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>久、視肉、【上虍下乎】交。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>其範林方三百里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>南祝融，獸身人面，乘兩龍。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海外西經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海外自西南陬西北陬者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>滅蒙鳥在結匈國北，為鳥青，赤尾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大運山高三百仞，在滅蒙鳥北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大樂之野，夏后啟于此?九代，乘兩龍，云蓋三層。左手操翳，右手操環，佩玉璜。在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大運山北。一曰大遺之野。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>三身國在夏后啟北，一首而三身。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>一臂國在其北，一臂、一目、鼻孔。有黃馬虎文，一目而一手。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>奇肱之國在其北。其人一臂三目，有陰有陽，乘文馬。有鳥焉，兩頭，赤黃色，在其旁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>形天與帝至此爭神，帝斷其首，葬之常羊之山。乃以乳為目，以臍為口，操幹戚以舞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>女祭、女戚在其北，居兩水間，戚操魚【魚旦】，祭操俎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【上次下鳥】鳥、【詹鳥】，其色青黃，所經國亡。在女祭北。【上次下鳥】鳥人面。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>居山上。一曰維鳥，青鳥、黃鳥所巢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>丈夫國在維鳥北，其為人衣冠帶劍。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>女醜之尸，生而十日炙殺之。在丈夫北。以右手鄣其面。十日居之，女醜居山之山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>巫咸國在女醜北，右手操青蛇，左手操赤蛇。在登葆山，群巫所從上下也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>並封在巫咸東，其狀如彘，前后皆有首，黑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>女子國在巫咸北，兩女子居，水周之。一曰居一門中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>軒轅之國在此窮山之際，其不壽者八百歲。在女子國北。人面蛇身，尾交首上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>窮山在其北，不敢西射，畏軒轅之丘。在軒轅國北。其丘方，四蛇盯繞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>此諸夭之野，鸞鳥自歌，鳳鳥自舞皇卵，民食之；甘露，民飲之：所欲自從也。百獸相</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>與群居。在四蛇北。其人兩手操卵食之，兩鳥居前導之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>龍魚陵居在其北，狀如狸。一曰【魚段】。即有神聖乘此以行九野。一曰鱉魚在夭野</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>北，其為魚也如鯉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>白民之國在龍魚北，白身披發。有乘黃，其狀如狐，其背上有角，乘之壽二千歲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>肅慎之國在白民北。有樹名曰雄常，先入伐帝，于此取之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>長股之國在雄常北，披發。一曰長腳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西方蓐收，左耳有蛇，乘兩龍。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海外北經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海外自東北陬至西北陬者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>無【綮糸換月】之國在長股東，為人無【綮糸換月】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>鐘山之神，名曰燭陰，視為晝，瞑為夜，吹為冬，呼為夏，不飲，不食，不息，息為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>風。身長千里。在無【綮糸換月】之東。其為物，人面，蛇身，赤色，居鐘山下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>一目國在其東，一目中其面而居。一曰有手足。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>柔利國在一目東，為人一手一足，反【左上木左下汆右□】，曲足居上。一云留利之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>國，人足反折。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>共工之臣曰相柳氏，九首，以食于九山。相柳之所抵，厥為澤溪。禹相柳，其血腥，不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>可以樹五谷種。禹厥之，三仞三沮，乃以為眾帝之台。在昆崙之北，柔利之東。相柳者，九</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>首人面，蛇身面青。不敢北射，畏共工之台。台在其東。台四方，隅有一蛇，虎色，首衝南</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>深目國在其東，為人舉一手一目。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>無腸之國在深目東，其為人長而無腸。聶耳之國在無腸國東，使兩文虎，為人兩手聶其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>耳。縣居海水中，及水所出入奇物。兩虎在其東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>誇父與日逐走，入日。渴欲得飲，飲于河渭，河渭不足，北飲大澤。未至，道渴而死。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>棄其杖。化為鄧林。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>博父國在聶耳東，其為人大，右手操青蛇，左手操黃蛇。鄧林在其東，二樹木。一曰博</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>父。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>禹所積石之山在其東，河水所入。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>拘纓之國在其東，一手把纓。一曰利纓之國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>尋木長千里，在拘纓南，生河上西北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【足支】踵國在拘纓東，其為人大，兩足亦大。一曰大踵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>歐絲之野大踵東，一女子跪據樹歐絲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>三桑無枝，在歐絲東，其木長百仞，無枝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>範林方三百里，在三桑東，洲環其下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>務隅之山，帝顓頊葬于陽，九嬪葬于陰。一曰爰有熊、羆、文虎、離朱、【丘鳥】久、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>視肉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>平丘在三桑東。爰有遺玉、青鳥、視肉、楊柳、甘【木且】、甘華，百果所生。有兩山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>夾上谷，二大丘居中，名曰平丘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>北海內有獸，其狀如馬，名曰【馬萄】【馬余】。有獸焉，其名曰【馬交】，狀如白</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>馬，鋸牙，食虎豹。有素獸焉，狀如馬，名曰蛩蛩。有青獸焉，狀如虎，我曰羅羅。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>北方禺強，人面鳥身，珥兩青蛇。踐兩青蛇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海外東經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海外自東南陬至東北陬者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【長差】丘，爰有遺玉、青馬、視肉、楊柳、甘華。甘果所生，在東海。兩山夾丘，上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有樹木。一曰嗟丘。一曰百果所在，在堯葬東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大人國在其北，為人大，坐而削船。一曰在【長差】丘北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>奢比尸國在其北，獸身、人面、大耳，珥兩青蛇。一曰肝榆之尸在大人北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>君子國在其北，衣冠帶劍，食獸，使二大虎在旁，其人好讓不爭。有薰華草，朝生夕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>死。一曰在肝榆之尸北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【上工下蟲】【上工下蟲】在其北，各有兩首。一曰在君子國北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>朝陽之谷，神曰天吳，是為水伯。在【上工下蟲】【上工下蟲】北兩水間。其為獸也，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>八首人面，八足八尾，皆青黃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>青丘國在其北，其狐四足九尾。一曰在朝陽北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>帝命豎亥步，自東極至于西極，五億十選九千八百步。豎亥右手把算，左手指青丘北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>一曰禹令豎亥。一曰五億十萬九千八百步。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>黑齒國在其北，為人黑，食稻啖蛇，一赤一青，在其旁。一曰在豎亥北，為人黑首，食</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>稻使蛇，其一蛇赤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>下有湯谷。湯谷上有扶桑，十日所浴，在黑齒北。居水中，有大木，九日居下枝，一日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>居上枝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>雨師妾在其北。其為人黑，兩手各操一蛇，左耳有青蛇，右耳有赤蛇。一曰在十日北，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>為人黑身人面，各操一龜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>玄股之國在其北。其為人衣魚食，使兩鳥夾之。一曰在雨師妾北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>毛民之國在其北，為人身生毛。一曰在玄股北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>勞民國在其北，其為人黑。或曰教民。一曰在毛民北，為人面目手足盡黑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東方句芒，鳥身人面，乘兩龍。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>建平元年四月丙戊，待詔太常屬臣望校治，侍中光祿勛臣龔，侍中奉車都尉光祿大夫臣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>秀領主省。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海內南經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海內東南陬以西者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>甌居海中。閩在海中，其西北有山。一曰閩中山在海中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>三天子鄣山在閩西海北。一曰在海中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>桂林八樹在番隅東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>伯慮國、離耳國、雕題國、北朐國皆在鬱水南。鬱水出湘陵南海。一曰相慮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>梟陽國在北朐之西。其為人人面長唇，黑身有毛，反踵，見人笑亦笑手操管。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>兕在舜葬東，湘水南。其狀如牛，蒼黑，一角。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>蒼梧之山，帝舜葬于陽，帝丹朱葬于陰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>泛林方三百里，在東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>兕兕知人名，其為獸如豕而人面，在舜葬西。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>兕兕西北有犀牛，其狀如牛而黑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>夏后啟之臣曰孟塗，是司神于巴。人請訟于孟塗之所，其衣有血者乃執之。是請生，在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>丹山西。丹山在丹陽南，丹陽居屬也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【上穴下契】窳龍首，居弱水中，在兕兕知人名之西，其狀如龍首，食人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有木，其狀如牛，引之有皮，若纓、黃蛇。其葉如羅，其實如欒，其木若【上□下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>區】，其名曰建木。在窳西弱水上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>氐人國在建木西，其為人人面而魚身，無足。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>巴蛇食象，三歲而出其骨，君子服之，無心腹之疾。其為蛇青赤黑。一曰黑蛇青首，在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>犀牛西。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>旄馬，其狀如馬，四節有毛。在巴蛇西北，高山南。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>匈奴、開題之國。列人之國並在西北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">大荒南經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">南海之外，赤水之西，流沙之東，有獸，左右有首，名曰【足術】踢。有三青獸相並，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>名曰雙雙。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有阿山者。南海之中，有泛天之山，赤水窮焉。赤水之東，有蒼梧之野，舜與叔均之所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>葬也。爰有文貝、離俞、【丘鳥】久、鷹、賈、委維、熊、羆、象、虎、豹、狼、視肉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有榮山、榮水出焉。黑水之南，有玄蛇，食【上鹿下主】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有巫山者，西行黃鳥。帝藥，八齋。黃鳥于巫山，司此玄蛇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有不庭之山，榮水窮焉。有人三身，帝俊妻娥皇，生此三身之國，姚姓，黍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>食，使四鳥。有淵四方，四隅皆送，北屬黑水，南屬大荒。北旁名曰少和之淵，南旁名曰從</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>淵，舜之所浴也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又有成山，甘水窮焉。有季禺之國，顓頊之子，食黍。有羽民之國，其民皆生毛羽。有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>卵之國，其民皆生卵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有不姜之山，黑水窮焉。又有賈山，汔水出焉。又有言山。又有登備之山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有恝恝之山。又有蒲山，澧水出焉。又有隗山，其西有丹，其東有玉。又南有山，漂水出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>焉。有尾山。有翠山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有盈民之國，於姓，黍食。又有人方食木葉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有不死之國，阿姓，甘木是食。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰去【外□內至】。南極果，北不成，去【外□內至】果。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>南海渚中，有神，人面，珥兩青蛇，踐兩赤蛇，曰不廷胡余。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有神名曰因因乎－－南方曰因乎，誇風曰乎民－－處南極以出入風。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有襄山。又有重陰之山。有人食獸，曰季厘。帝俊生季厘，故曰季厘之國。有緡淵。少</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>昊生倍伐降處緡淵。有水四方，名曰俊壇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有【載車換至】民之國。帝舜生無淫，降【載車換至】處，是謂巫【載車換至】民。巫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【載車換至】民盼姓，食谷，不績不經，服也；不稼不穡，食也。愛歌舞之鳥，鸞鳥自歌，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>鳳鳥自舞。爰有百獸，相群爰處。百谷所聚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰融天，海水南入焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有人曰鑿齒，有蜮山者，有蜮民之國，桑姓，食黍，射蜮是食。有人方【□幹】弓射黃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>蛇，名曰蜮人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有宋山者，有赤蛇，名曰育蛇。有木生山上，名曰楓木。楓木，【嗤去口】尤所棄其桎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>梏，是為楓木。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有人方齒虎尾，名曰祖狀之尸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有小人，名曰焦僥之國，幾姓，嘉谷是食。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名【朽木換歹】塗之山，青水窮焉。有云雨之山，有木名曰欒。禹攻云</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>雨。有赤石焉生欒，黃本，赤枝，青葉，群帝焉取藥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有國曰顓頊，生伯服，食黍。有鼬姓之國。有苕山。又有宗山。又有姓山，又有壑山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又有陳州山，又有東州山。又有白水山，白水出焉，而生白淵，昆吾之師所浴也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有人名曰張宏，在海上捕魚。海中有張宏之國，食魚，使四鳥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有人焉，鳥喙，有翼，方捕魚于海。大荒之中，有人名曰【灌□換馬】頭。鯀妻士敬，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>士敬子曰琰融，生【灌□換馬】頭。頭人面鳥喙，有翼，食海中魚，杖翼而行。維宜芑苣，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【□換禾】是食。有【灌□換馬】頭之國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>帝堯、帝嚳、帝舜葬于岳山。爰有文貝、離俞、【丘鳥】久、鷹、廷維、視肉、熊、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>羆、虎、豹；朱木、青華，玄實。有申山者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰天台高山，海水入焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東南海之外，甘水之間，有羲和之國，有女子名曰羲和，方日浴于甘淵。羲和者，帝俊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>之妻，生十日。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有蓋猶之山者，其上有甘【木且】，枝幹皆赤，黃葉，白華，黑實。東又有甘華，枝幹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>皆赤，黃葉。有青馬，有赤馬，名曰三騅。有視肉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有小人，名曰菌人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有南類之山。爰有遺玉、青馬、三騅、視肉、甘華。百谷所在。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海內西經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海內西南陬以北者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>貳負之臣曰危，危與貳負殺囗【上穴下契】窳。帝乃梏之疏屬之山，桎其右足，反縛兩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>手與發，系之山上木。在開題西北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大澤方百里，群鳥所生及所解。在雁門北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>雁門山，雁出其間。在氐國西。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>高柳在代北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>后稷之葬，山水環之。在氐國西。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>流黃酆氏之國，中方三百里；有塗四方，中有山。在后稷葬西。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>流沙出鐘山，西行又南行昆崙之虛，西南入海，黑水之山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東胡在大澤東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>夷人在東胡東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>貊國在漢水東北。地近于燕，滅之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>孟鳥在貊國東北。其鳥文赤、黃、青，東鄉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>海內昆崙之虛，在西北，帝之下都。昆崙之虛，方八百里，高萬仞。上有木禾，長五</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>尋，大五圍。而有九井，以玉為檻。面有九門，門有開明獸守之，百神之所在。在八隅之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>岩，赤水之際，非仁羿莫能上岡之岩。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>赤水出東南隅，以行其東北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>河水出東北隅，以行其北，西南又入渤海，又出海外，即西而北，入禹所導積石山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>洋水、黑水出西北隅，以東，東行，又東北，南入海，羽民南。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>弱水、青水出西南隅，以東，又北，又西南，過畢方鳥東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>昆崙南淵深三百仞。開明獸身大類虎而九首，皆人面，東向立昆崙上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>開明西有鳳凰、鸞鳥，皆戴蛇踐蛇，膺有赤蛇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>開明北有視肉、珠樹、文玉樹、囗【王幹】琪樹、不死樹。鳳凰、鸞鳥皆戴【拔□換</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>盾】。又有離朱、木禾、柏樹、甘水、聖木曼兌，一曰挺木牙交。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>開明東有巫彭、巫抵、巫陽、巫履、巫凡、巫相，夾【上穴下契】窳之尸，皆操不死之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>藥以距之。【上穴下契】窳者，蛇身人面，貳負臣所殺也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>服常樹，其上有三頭人，伺琅【王幹】樹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>開明南有樹鳥，六首；蛟、蝮、蛇、【蟲隹】、豹、鳥秩樹，于表池樹木，誦鳥、【隼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>鳥】視肉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海內北經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海內西北陬以東者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>蛇巫之山，上有人操【木丕】而東向立。一曰龜山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西王母梯幾而戴勝杖。其南有三青鳥，為西王母取食。在昆崙虛北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有人曰大行伯，把戈。其東有犬封國。貳負之尸在大行伯東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>犬封國曰大戎國，狀如犬。有一女子，方跪進【木丕】食。有文馬，縞身朱【髻吉換</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>鼠】，目若黃金，名曰吉量，乘之壽千歲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>鬼國在貳負之尸北，為物人面而一目。一曰貳負神在其東，為物人而蛇身。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>犬如犬，青，食人從首始。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>窮奇狀如虎，有翼，食人從首始。所食被發。在犬北。一曰從足。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>帝堯台、帝嚳台、帝丹朱台、帝舜台，各二台，台四方，在昆崙東北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大蜂，其狀如螽；朱蛾，其狀如蛾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【蟲喬】，其為人虎文，脛有【綮糸換月】。在窮奇東。一曰狀如人，昆崙虛北所有。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【外門內上日內下羽】非，人面而獸身，青色。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>據比之尸，其為人折頸披發，無一手。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>環狗，其為人獸首人身。一曰【蟲胃】狀如狗，黃色。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>襪，其為物，人身黑首從目。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>戎，其為人，人首三角。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>林氏國有珍獸，大若虎，五採畢具，尾長于身，名曰騶吾，乘之日行千里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>昆崙虛南所，有泛林方三百里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>從極之淵深三百仞，維冰夷恆都焉，，冰夷人面，乘兩龍。一曰忠極之淵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>陽汗之山，河山其中，凌門之山，河出其中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>王子夜之尸，兩手、兩股、胸、首、齒，皆斷異處。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>舜夷登比氏生宵明、燭光，處河大澤，二女之靈能照此所方百里。一曰登北氏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>蓋國在鉅燕南，倭北。倭屬燕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>朝鮮在列陽東，海北山南。列陽屬燕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>列姑射在海河州中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>射姑國在海中，屬列姑射。西南，山環之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大蟹在海中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>陵魚人面，手足，魚身，在海中。大【魚便】居海中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>明組邑居海中。逢萊山在海中。大人之市在海中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海內東經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海內東北陬以南者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>鉅燕在東北陬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>國在流沙中者【土享】端、璽【日奐】，在昆崙虛東南。一曰海內之郡，不為郡縣，在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>流沙中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>國在流沙外者，大夏、豎沙、居繇、月支之國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西胡白玉山在大夏東，蒼梧在白玉山西南，皆在流沙西，昆崙虛東南。昆崙山在西胡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西。皆在西北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>雷澤中有雷神，龍首而人頭，鼓其腹。在吳西。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>都州在海中。一曰鬱州。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>琅邪台在渤海間，琅邪之東。其北有山，一曰在海間。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>韓雁在海中，都州南。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>始鳩在海中，轅厲南。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>會稽山在大楚南。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>岷三江，首大江出汶山，北江出曼山，南江出高山。高山在城都西，入海，在長州南。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>浙江出三天子都，在其東。在閩西北，入海，余暨南。廬江出三天子都，入江，彭澤西。一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>曰天子鄣。淮水出余山，余山在朝陽東，義鄉西。入海，淮浦北。湘水出舜葬東南陬，西環</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>之。入洞庭下。一曰東南西澤。漢水出鮒魚之山，帝顓頒葬于陽，九嬪葬陰，西蛇衛之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【□蒙】水出漢陽西，入江，聶耳西。溫水出崆峒山，在臨汾南，入河華陽北。穎水出少</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>室，少室山在雍氏南，入淮西鄢北。一曰緱氏。汝水出天息山，在梁勉鄉西南，入淮極西</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>北。一曰淮在期思北。涇水出長城北山，山在鬱郅長垣北，北入渭。戲北。渭水出鳥鼠同穴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>山，東注河，入華陰北。白水出蜀，而東南注江，入江州城下。沅水山出像郡鐔城西，入東</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>注江，入下雋西，合洞庭中。贛水出聶都東山，東北注江，入彭澤西。泗水出魯東北，而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>南，西南過湖陵西，而東南注東海，入淮陰北。鬱水出象郡，而西南注南海，入須陵東南。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>肄水出臨晉西南，而東南注海，入番禺西。潢水出桂陽西北山，東南注肄水，入敦浦西。洛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>水出洛西山，東北注河，入成皋之西。汾之出上窳北，而西南注河，入皮氏南。沁水出井陘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>山東，東南注河，入懷東南。濟水出共山南東丘，絕鉅鹿澤，注渤海，入潦陽。【上虍下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>乎】沱水出晉陽城南，而西至陽曲北，而東注渤海，入越章武北。漳水出山陽東，東注渤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>海，入章武南。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">大荒東經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">東海之外大壑，少昊之國。少吳孺帝顓頊于此，棄其琴瑟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有甘山者，甘水出焉，生甘淵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒東南隅有，名皮母地丘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東海之外，大荒之中，有山名曰大言，日月所出。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有波谷山者，有大人之國。有大人之市，名曰大人之堂。有一大人【俊□換足】其上，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>張其兩耳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有小人國，名靖人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有神，人面獸身，名曰【黎汆換牛】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有【橘木換□】山，楊水出焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有【上□下為】國，黍食，使四鳥：虎、豹、熊、羆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰合虛，日月所出。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有中容之國。帝俊生中容，中容人食獸、木實，使四鳥：豹、虎、熊、羆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有東口之山。有君子之國，其人衣冠帶劍。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有司幽之國。帝俊生晏龍，晏龍生司幽，司幽生思土，不妻；思女，不夫。食黍，食</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>獸，是使四鳥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有大阿之山者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒中有山，名曰明星，日月所出。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有白民之國。帝俊生帝鴻，帝鴻生白民，白民銷姓，黍食，使四鳥：豹、虎、熊、羆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有青丘之國，有狐，九尾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有柔僕民，是維嬴土之國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有黑齒之國。帝俊生黑齒，姜姓，囗食，使四鳥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有夏州之國。有蓋余之國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有神人，八首人面，虎身十尾，名曰天吳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰鞠陵于天、東極、離瞀，日月所出。名曰折丹－－東方曰折，來風</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>曰俊－－處東極以出入風。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東海之渚中，有神，人面鳥身，珥兩黃蛇，踐兩黃蛇，名曰禺【豸虎】。黃帝生禺【豸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>虎】，禺【豸虎】生禺京。禺京處北海，禺【豸虎】處東海，是惟海神。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有招搖山，融水出焉。有國曰玄股，黍食，使四鳥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有困民國，勾姓而食。有人曰王亥，兩手操鳥，方食其頭。王亥托于有易、河伯僕牛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有易潛出，為國于獸，方食之，名曰搖民。帝舜生戲，戲生搖民。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>海內有兩人，名曰女醜。女醜有大蟹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰孽搖【君頁】羝。上有扶木，柱三百里，其葉如芥。有谷曰溫源</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>谷。湯谷上有扶木，一曰方至，一曰方出，皆載于烏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有神，人面、犬耳、獸身，珥兩青蛇，名曰奢比尸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有五採之鳥，相鄉棄沙。惟帝俊下友。帝下兩壇，採鳥是司。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰猗天蘇山，日月所生。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有【土熏】民之國。有綦山。又有搖山。有【融蟲換曾】山，又有門戶山，又有盛山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又有待山。有五採之鳥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東荒之中，有山名曰壑明俊疾，日月所出。有中容之國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東北海中，又有三青馬、三騅、甘華。愛有遺玉、三青鳥、三騅、視肉、甘華、甘【木</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>且】。百谷所在。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有女和月母之國。有人名曰【上鳥下宛】－－北方曰【上鳥下宛】，來之風曰【□炎】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>－－是處東極隅以止日月，使無相間出沒，司其短長。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒東北隅中，有山名曰凶犁土丘。應龍處南極，殺【嗤去口】尤與誇父，不得複上，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>故下數旱。旱而為應龍之狀，乃得大雨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>東海中有流波山，入海七千里。其上有獸，狀如牛，蒼身而無角，一足，出入水則必風</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>雨，其光如日月，其聲如雷，其名曰夔。黃帝得之，以其皮為鼓，橛以雷獸之骨，聲聞五百</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>里，以威天下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">大荒西經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">西北海之外，大荒之隅，有山而不合，名曰不周負子，有兩黃獸守之。有水曰寒署之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>水。水西有濕山，水東有幕山。有禹攻共工國山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有國名曰淑士，顓頊之子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有神十人，名曰女媧之腸，化為神，處慄廣之野；橫道而處。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有人名曰石夷，來風曰韋，處西北隅以司日月之長短。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有五採之鳥，有冠，名曰狂鳥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有大澤之長山。有白氏之國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西北海之外，赤水東，有長脛之國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有西周之國，姬姓，食谷。有人方耕，名曰叔均。帝俊生后稷，稷降以谷。稷之曰台</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>璽，生叔均。叔均是代其父及稷播百谷，始作耕。有赤國妻氏。有雙山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西海之外，大荒之中，有方山者，上有青樹，名曰櫃格之松，日月所出入也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西北海之外，赤水之西，有先民之國，食谷，使四鳥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有北狄之國。黃帝之孫曰始均，始均生北狄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有芒山。有桂山。有【搖□換木】山，其上有人，號曰太子長琴。顓頊生老童，老童生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>祝融，祝融生太子長琴，是處【搖□換木】山，始作樂風。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有五採鳥三名：一曰皇鳥，一曰鸞鳥，一曰鳳鳥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有蟲狀如菟，胸以后者裸不見，青如【□爰】狀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰豐沮玉門，日月所入。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有靈山，巫咸、巫即、巫盼、巫彭、巫姑、巫真、巫禮、巫抵、巫謝、巫羅十巫，從此</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>升降，百藥爰在。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西有王母之山，壑山、海山。有沃之國，沃民是處。沃之野，鳳鳥之卵是食，甘露是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>飲。凡其所欲其味盡存。爰有甘華、璇瑰、甘【木且】、瑤碧、白木、白柳、視肉、琅【王</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>千】、白丹、青丹、多銀鐵。鸞鳳自歌，鳳鳥自舞，爰有百獸，相群是處，是謂沃之野。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有三青鳥，赤首黑目，一名曰大【黎汆換鳥】，一曰少【黎汆換鳥】，一名曰青鳥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有軒轅之台，射者不敢西向射，畏軒轅之台。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有龍山，日月所入。有三澤水，名曰三淖，昆吾之所食也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有人衣青，以袂蔽面，名曰女醜之尸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有女子之國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有桃山。有【上亡下蟲】山。有桂山。有于土山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有丈夫之國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有【上合下廾】州之國，五採之鳥仰天，名曰鳴鳥。爰有百樂歌舞之鳳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有軒轅之國。江山之南棲為吉。不壽者乃八百歲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西海【□肴】中，有神，人面鳥身，珥兩青蛇，踐兩赤蛇，名曰【上合下廾】茲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰日月山，天樞也。吳【女巨】天門，日月所入。有神，人面無臂，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>兩足反屬于頭山，名曰【口虛】。顓頊生老童，老童生重及黎，帝令重獻上天，令黎邛下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>地。下地是生噎，處于西極，以行日月星辰之行次。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有人反臂，名曰天虞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有女子方浴月。帝俊妻常羲，生月十有二，此始浴之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>行玄丹之山。有五色之鳥，人面有發。爰有青【上文下鳥】、黃【上敖下鳥】、青鳥、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>黃鳥，其所集者其國亡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有池，名孟翼之攻顓頊之池。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰鏖鏊鉅，日月所入者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有獸，左右有首，名曰屏蓬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有巫山者。有壑山者。有金門之山，有人名曰黃【女巨】之尸。有比翼之鳥。有白鳥，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>青翼，黃尾，玄喙。有赤犬，名曰天犬，其所下者有兵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西海之南，流沙之濱，赤水之后，黑水之前，有大山，名曰昆崙之丘。有神，人面虎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>身，有文有尾，皆白，處之。其下有弱水之淵環之，其外有炎火之山，投物輒然。有人戴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>勝，虎齒，有豹尾，穴處，名曰西王母。此山萬物盡有。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰常陽之山，日月所入。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有寒荒之國。有二人女祭、女囗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有壽麻之國。南岳娶州山女，名曰女虔。女虔生季格，季格生壽麻。壽麻正立無景，疾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>呼無響。爰有大暑，不可以往。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有人無首，操戈盾立，名曰夏耕之尸。故成湯伐夏桀于章山，克之，斬耕厥前。耕既</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>立，無首，【足口換禾】厥咎，乃降于巫山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有人名曰吳回，奇左，是無右臂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有蓋山之國。有樹，赤皮枝幹，青葉，名曰朱木。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有一臂民。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山，名曰大荒之山，日月所入。有人焉三面，是顓頊之子，三面一臂，三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>面之人不死。是謂大荒之野。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西南海之外，赤水之南，流沙之西，有人珥兩青蛇，乘兩龍，名曰夏后開。開上三嬪于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>天，得《九辯》與《九歌》以下。此天穆之野，高二千仞，開焉得始歌《九招》。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有互人之國。炎帝之孫名曰靈恝生百互人，是能上下于天。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有魚偏枯，名曰魚婦。顓頊死即複蘇。風道北來，天及大水泉，蛇乃化為魚，是為魚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>婦。顓頊死即複蘇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有青鳥，身黃，赤足，六首，名曰【鳥蜀】鳥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有大巫山。有金之山。西南，大荒之中隅，有偏句、常羊之山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">大荒北經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">東南海之外，大荒之中，河水之間，附禺之山，帝顓頊與九嬪葬焉。爰有【丘鳥】久、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>文貝、離俞、鸞鳥、皇鳥、大物、小物。有青鳥、琅鳥、玄鳥、黃鳥、虎、豹、熊、羆、黃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>蛇、視肉、【王千】瑰、瑤碧，皆出衛于山。丘方員三百里，丘南帝俊竹林在焉，大可為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>舟。竹南有赤澤水，名曰封淵。有三桑無枝。丘西有沈淵，顓頊所浴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有胡不與之國，烈姓，黍食。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰不咸，有肅慎氏之國。蜚蛭，四翼。有蟲，獸身蛇身，名曰琴蟲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有人名曰大人。有大人之國，厘姓，黍食。有大青蛇，黃頭，食【上鹿下主】。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有榆山。有鯀攻程州之山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰衡天。有先民之山。有【上般下木】木千里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有叔【蜀欠】國，顓頊之子，黍食，使四鳥：虎、豹、熊、羆。有黑蟲如熊狀，名曰獵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>獵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有北齊之國，姜姓，使虎、豹、熊、羆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰先檻大逢之山，河濟所入，海北注焉。其西有山，名曰禹所積石。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有陽山者。有順山者，順水出焉。有始州之國，有丹山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有大澤方千里，群鳥所解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有毛民之國，依姓，食黍，使四鳥。禹生均國，均國生役採，役採生修【革台】，修</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【革台】殺綽人。帝念之，潛為之國，是此毛民。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有儋耳之國，任姓禺號子，食谷。北海之渚中，有神，人面鳥身，珥兩青蛇，踐兩赤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>蛇，名曰禺強。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰北極天櫃，海水北注焉。有神，九首人面鳥身，名曰九鳳。又有神</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>銜蛇銜操蛇，其狀虎首人身，四蹄長肘，名曰強良。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000000999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有山名曰成都載天。有人珥兩黃蛇，把兩黃蛇，名曰誇父。后土生信，信生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>誇父。誇父不量力，欲追日景，逮之于禺谷。將飲河而不足也，將走大澤，未至，死于此。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>應龍已殺【嗤去口】尤，又殺誇父，乃去南方處之，故南方多雨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又有無腸國，是任姓。無繼子，食魚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>共工臣名曰相繇，九首蛇身，自環，食于九土。其所【鳥欠】所尼，即為源澤，不辛乃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>苦，百獸莫能處。禹湮洪水，殺相繇，其血腥臭，不可生谷；其地多水，不可居也。禹湮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>之，三仞三沮，乃以為池，群帝因是以為台。在昆崙之北。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有岳之山。尋竹生焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有名山曰不句，海水入焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有系昆之山者，有共工之台，射者不敢北射。有人衣青衣，名曰黃帝女魃。【嗤去口】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>尤作兵伐黃帝，黃帝乃令應龍攻之冀州之野。應龍畜水。【嗤去口】尤請風伯雨師，縱大風</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>雨。黃帝乃下天女曰魃，雨止，遂殺【嗤去口】尤。魃不得複上，所居不雨。叔均言之帝，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>后置之赤水之北。叔均乃為田祖。魃時亡之，所欲逐之者，令曰：“神北行！”先除水道，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>決通溝瀆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有人方食魚，名曰深目民之國，盼姓，食魚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有鐘山者。有女子衣青衣，名曰赤水女子獻。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中。有山名曰融父山，順水入焉。有人名曰犬戎。黃帝生苗龍，苗龍，苗龍生融</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>吾，融吾生弄明，弄明生白犬，白犬有牝牡，是為犬戎，肉食。有赤獸，馬狀無首，名曰戎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>宣王尸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有山名曰齊州之山、君山、【上兩先下鬲】山、鮮野山、魚山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有人一目，當面中生。一曰是威姓，少昊之子，食黍。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有繼無民，繼無民任姓，無骨子，食氣、魚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西北海外，流沙之東，有國曰中【車扁】，顓頊之子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有國名曰賴丘。有犬戎國。有神，人面獸身，名曰犬戎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西北海外，黑水之北，有人有翼，名曰苗民。顓頊生【灌□換馬】頭，【灌□換馬】頭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>生苗民，苗民厘姓，食肉。有山名曰章山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>大荒之中，有衡石山、九陰山、洞野之山，上有赤樹，青葉赤華，名曰若木。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有牛黎之國。有人無骨，儋耳之子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西北海之外，赤水之北，有章尾山。有神，人面蛇身而赤，直目正乘，其瞑乃晦，其視</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>乃明，不食不寢不息，風雨是謁。是燭九陰，是燭龍。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">海內經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">東海之內，北海之隅，有國名曰朝鮮；天毒，其人水居，偎人愛之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西海之內，流沙之中，有國名曰壑市。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西海之內，流沙之西，有國名曰泛葉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>流沙之西，有鳥山者，三水出焉。爰有黃金、【王千】瑰、丹貨、銀鐵，皆流于此中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又有淮山，好水出焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>流沙之東，黑水之西，有朝云之國、司彘之國。黃帝妻雷祖，生昌意。昌意降處若水，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>生韓流。韓流擢首、謹耳、人面、豕喙、麟身、渠股、豚止，取淖子曰阿女，生帝顓頊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>流沙之東，黑水之間，有山名曰有死之山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>華山青水之東，有山名曰肇山。有人名曰柏高，柏高上下于此，至于天。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西南黑水之間，有都廣之野，后稷葬焉。爰有膏菽、膏稻、膏黍、膏稷，百谷自生，冬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>夏播琴。鸞鳥自歌，鳳鳥自?，靈壽實華，草木所聚。爰有百獸，相群爰處。此草也，冬夏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>不死。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>南海之外，黑水青水之間，有木名曰叵木，若水出焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有禺中之國。有列襄之國。有靈山，有赤蛇在木上，名曰【左蟲右上而右下大】蛇，木</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>食。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有鹽長之國。有人焉鳥首，名曰鳥氏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有九丘，以水絡之：名曰陶唐之丘、有叔得之丘、孟盈之丘、昆吾之丘、黑白之丘、赤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>望之丘、參衛之丘、武夫之丘、神民之丘。有木，青葉紫莖，玄華黃實，百仞無枝，有九</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>【木屬】，下有九枸，其實如麻，其葉如芒。大【白皋】爰過，黃帝所為。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有【上穴下契】窳，龍首，是食人。有青獸，人面，名是曰猩猩。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>西南有巴國。大【白皋】生咸鳥，咸鳥生乘厘，乘厘生后照，后照是始為巴人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有國名曰流黃辛氏，其域中方三百里，其出是塵土。有巴遂山，澠水出焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又有朱卷之國。有黑蛇，青首，食象。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>南方有贛巨人，人面長臂，黑身有毛，反踵，見人笑亦笑，唇蔽其面，因即逃也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又有黑人，虎首鳥足，兩手持蛇，方【餡□換口】之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有嬴民，鳥足，有封豕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有人曰苗民。有神焉，人首蛇身，長如轅，左右有首，衣紫衣，冠旃冠，名曰延維，人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>主得而饗食之，伯天下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有鸞鳥自歌，鳳鳥自舞。鳳鳥首文曰德，翼文曰順，膺文曰仁，背文曰義，見則天下和。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>又有青獸如菟，名曰【上山下j抗罰□洩鶘健Ｓ寫淠瘛Ｓ鋅啄瘛□br&gt; 南海之內，有衡山，有菌山，有桂山。有山名三天子之都。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>南方蒼梧之丘，蒼梧之淵，其中有九嶷山，舜之所葬，在長沙零陵界中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>北海之內，有蛇山者，蛇水出焉，東入于海。有五採之鳥，飛蔽一鄉，名曰翳鳥。又有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>不距之山，巧【□垂】葬其西。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>北海之內，有反縛盜械、帶戈常倍之佐，各曰相顧之尸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>伯夷父生西岳，西岳生先龍，先龍是始生氐羌，氐羌乞姓。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>北海之內，有山，名曰幽都之山，黑水出焉。其上有玄鳥、玄蛇、玄狐蓬尾。有大玄之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>山。有玄丘之民。有大幽之國。有赤脛之民。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>有釘靈之國，其民從【漆左□換右□】以下有毛，馬蹄善走。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>炎帝之孫伯陵，伯陵同吳權之妻阿女緣婦，緣婦孕三年，是生鼓、延、殳。始為侯，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>鼓、延是始為鐘，為樂風。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>黃帝生駱明，駱明生白馬，白馬是為鯀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>帝俊生禺號，禺號生淫梁，淫梁生番禺，是始為舟。番禺生奚仲，奚仲生吉光，吉光是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>始以木為車。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>少【白皋】生般，般是始為弓矢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>帝俊賜羿彤弓素【矢曾】，以扶下國，羿是始去恤下地之百艱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>帝俊生晏龍，晏龍是為琴瑟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>帝俊有子八人，三身生義均，義均是始為巧【□垂】，是始作下民百巧。后稷是播百</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>谷。稷之孫曰叔均，是始作牛耕。大比赤陰，是始為國。禹、鯀是始布土，定九州。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>炎帝之妻，赤水之子聽【□夭】生炎居，炎居生節並，節並生戲器，戲器生祝融。祝融</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>降處于江水，生共工。共工生術器，術器首方顛，是複土穰，以處江水。共工生后土，后土</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>生噎鳴，噎鳴生歲十有二。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>洪水滔天。鯀竊帝之息壤以堙洪水，不待帝命。帝命祝融殺鯀于羽郊。鯀複生禹。帝乃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p>命禹卒布土以定九州。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/bcd2ddc4282500e0/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-f09fcd twpub-bcd2ddc4282500e0-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">End of Project Gutenberg's Classic of the Mountains and Seas, by Anonymous</p></div>"
        },
